I take it you've been
enjoying yourselves?
gacha_serif1: Well, I'm sorry to hear that. But there's no time to make it up to you.

name: Wagnas
flavor_text: The end of the world draws near, but to ignore the imminent threat of the termites would result in our total extermination. We should be saving people first. Is that not the obvious choice?
gacha_text: We should be saving people first. Is that not the obvious choice?

name: Wagnas
flavor_text: Sometimes strong, and sometimes gentle. Magnificent notes are born of a certain lightness. The savage skills of battle alone do not make a hero. A hero is a hero only when there is beauty.
gacha_text: A hero is a hero only when there is beauty.

name: Noel
flavor_text: I don't care for needless conflict. I'd prefer to talk things out. But if your mind is already made up, then there's no other choice, is there? Just know that I have no intention of handing you an easy victory.

name: Noel
flavor_text: Who did you defeat? You defeated a friend, with whom I was bound by blood. In other words, someone important to me. Now I will not hold back. I will kill you with the full extent of my power.
gacha_text: Do me a favor and let me kill you.
gacha_serif1: It's been a long time, Sagzaar.

name: Noel
flavor_text: I am a soldier. Soldiers exist solely to protect the people. But too many have lost their lives to you damn termites. So, I don't care what it is you are fighting for, I will not forgive you.
gacha_text: I don't care what it is you are fighting for, I will not forgive you.

name: Noel
flavor_text: I've gained my power by assimilating with monsters. And not just monsters... I've also slain and assimilated with heroes of many worlds. The Noel in me has dwindled. Yet still, I am Noel of the Seven Heroes.
gacha_text: I am Noel of the Seven Heroes.
gacha_serif1: You're the Emperor, right? I am Noel of the Seven Heroes.

name: Noel
flavor_text: A feast, drinks, and folks dressed to impress. This is far from a night of peace and quiet. Yet tomorrow, we fight for our lives against powerful enemies in another world. I'll take a night like this. Mayhap I'll even dance.
gacha_text: Mayhap I'll even dance.

name: Rocbouquet
flavor_text: All I want to do is help my brother and Wagnas. To that end, I have many things I must accomplish. Enough of your babbling, and get out of my way!

name: Rocbouquet
flavor_text: Brother, Wagnas, I am going to fight now. Please watch over me!
gacha_text: You'll be fighting for me from now on.
gacha_serif1: I can tell that you're really strong. Can I ask you a favor?

name: Rocbouquet
flavor_text: You're not going to tell me you don't need it, right? Right?!
gacha_text:
Why do I have to wear this
anyway?
gacha_serif1: ...Really? I guess it's fine then.

name: Rocbouquet
flavor_text: The one who can help Lord Wagnas is not I, but rather my brother, Lord Noel. The one Lord Wagnas first called for was not I, but Lord Noel. One day I hope I can serve Lord Wagnas, and be the one he requests first.
gacha_text: One day I hope I can serve Lord Wagnas, and be the one he requests first.

name: Rocbouquet
flavor_text: This odd little Daruma is supposed to bring good fortune. You can see both of its eyes! You must be lucky. Here, come closer. Rejoice, for I'm gonna turn you into a Daruma, too.

name: Rocbouquet
flavor_text: These little "squid" creatures are delectable. Such a waste to just kill them and not eat them. They're great fried or grilled, but I think they're best raw. From now on, I'll gulp them down alive. They should be grateful for my benevolence.
gacha_text: These little "squid" creatures are delectable.

name: Rocbouquet
flavor_text: You, too, crawl around this world like a maggot in flesh. I will do what I want, how I want. Only my big brother Noel is allowed to chime in, and I welcome it when Lord Wagnas does so. But you? You shut your mouth!
gacha_text: Stop talking.
gacha_serif1: You crawl around this world like a maggot in flesh. To the abyss!

name: Subier
flavor_text: I can handle the sea myself. I do not need your interference.

name: Subier
flavor_text: So, you've given me a calligraphy brush. All right, I'll write one word to express my hope for the new year: Sea!
gacha_text: The first calligraphy of the year! Exciting!
gacha_serif1: New Year's is great, and the drinks are free!

name: Subier
flavor_text: You do not understand what this form means. No, I do not need you to. It's pointless to tell you what is in my heart. You only need to be crushed by all my rage!
gacha_text: You only need to be crushed by all my rage!
gacha_serif1: Subier

name: Dantarg
flavor_text: Don't even bother showing yourselves, you pathetic creatures. You're not even worthy enough for me to crush beneath my feet.

name: Dantarg
flavor_text: You dare stand before me? Very well. It's been a long time since I've had worthy adversaries. I'll crush you!
gacha_text:
You're in no position
to threaten me!
gacha_serif1:
Don't make me regret it.
As long as you continue to behave yourself here, I'll leave you alone, Dantarg.
gacha_serif2: What? Did I hear that right? You're just going to let me go?

name: Dantarg
flavor_text: Fight. Fight someone strong. Fight someone stronger. That is my purpose in life. I don't need a reason to fight. Are you strong? Fight me, then.
gacha_text: I will rage to the fullest until I've had my fill.

name: Bokhohn
flavor_text: I am just a small fry. One look at me and that much should be obvious. So please, let me go.

name: Bokhohn
flavor_text: To emerge so nonchalantly at this stage... You clearly lack any strategy. Let us begin, then. Your mistake will be your downfall!
gacha_text:
Was it part of your plan to come
after me last?
gacha_serif1: You naive fool!

name: Bokhohn
flavor_text: Did you think I could only manipulate dolls and people? I can also manipulate animals, of course. I think I'll use this sleigh to drop some presents across Avalon!
gacha_text: You want a present?

name: Kzinssie
flavor_text: I am Kzinssie of the Seven Heroes. The strongest of the Heroes. I am the strongest! If you fear me, then run. You wish to stay? Then you shall die. Soulsteal!

name: Kzinssie
flavor_text: I've always been strong. Wagnas and Noel were both scared to even look me in the eye. When they asked me to join the Seven Heroes, I felt generous and said yes.
gacha_text:
I was getting tired of waiting.
Let's start already!
gacha_serif1: A-again!

name: Kzinssie
flavor_text: What is this sensation? Power is gathering about me. Is this the power of the demon I absorbed? Excellent. With such power, no one can stand against me.
gacha_text: You used assimilation magic as well, didn't you?

name: Julian
flavor_text: You might be wondering how capable I really am, but trust me, no one's more devoted to defending Sinon than me. This is where my younger sister was born and where she died.

name: Julian
flavor_text: You're probably thinking "Look at this weak pretty boy" or something, huh? Wanna say hi to my fist? We'll find out how weak this "pretty boy" really is.

name: Julian
flavor_text: I see you came dressed for the occasion. I did my best to clean up nicely too. Let's forget about who we usually are. Tonight, we can pretend to be cool, right?
gacha_text:
Lady Monika, it's freezing
out here. Could you maybe
make it quick?

name: Julian
flavor_text: Thanks for the chocolates. These are from me and are for you and you alone. Seriously, you really are the only one getting these. I'm no two-timer.

name: Julian
flavor_text: Me, in the Princess Guard! I knew Lord Mikhail recognized talent. I've earned Lady Monika's trust, too. These bigwigs, they're different. Ellen's sure to look at me in a new light!
gacha_text: No problem! I guess...

name: Julian
flavor_text: The wind has grown colder. Winter is coming. The cold is nice, but only when you have someone to keep you warm. I hope I can see the girls I met at the beach and that Slime girl again!
gacha_text: I hope I can see those girls again!

name: Thomas
flavor_text: To be a leader with the right attitude, always looking ahead, living up to expectations. Such is the duty of those born with the Bent family name. I've yet to become such a person. But one day I shall. This I swear on my family's name.

name: Thomas
flavor_text: If Loanne is once again under threat, then I too shall fight. There's nothing special about this. After all, we felt the same way the last time this happened.
gacha_text:
I hope our paths
will cross again.
gacha_serif1: I'm joining a newly formed escort squad for Lady Monika.
gacha_serif2: I'll be heading for Pidona now.

name: Thomas
flavor_text: Stone. Wood. Hides. Paper. What makes a book has changed, but they've always been an important vehicle for crafting the future of civilization. Read a book and transcend time!
gacha_text:
If there's anything I
can do... anything
at all.
gacha_serif1: Young Thomas. Thank you for coming. Welcome to Pidona.

name: Thomas
flavor_text: I've polished myself as much as a Bent can. There will come a time when I'll have to put it to the test, and I will learn my true worth. Yes, the time has come.
gacha_text: Life always finds a way to prevail!
gacha_serif1: Life always finds a way to prevail!

name: Mikhail
flavor_text: There are those who seek to depose me, to take over this country. This is a golden opportunity. I'll round up all of them, including my other detractors, and defeat them once and for all. Then, I'll unite Loanne under one banner. All before the Sinistrals return.

name: Mikhail
flavor_text: Byunei's forces are marching on Loanne. I will lead the fight against them. The enemies will be routed. I will not let them lay a finger on the people of Loanne!
gacha_text:
Hmph. So be it.
Then follow me
to the ends of the Abyss!
gacha_serif1: There's no reason for you to risk your life, Khalid. Good work.

name: Mikhail
flavor_text: This banquet is to celebrate everyone's achievements. Your attire is formal yet not overly extravagant, and your figure and demeanor are already perfect. And above all, you're beautiful... ly dressed, I mean.
gacha_text:
I wish you can
continue your efforts.
gacha_serif1: Last but not least, there's one other warrior whose splendid courage I wish to acknowledge.

name: Mikhail
flavor_text: I will spare no effort and shed any blood to see Loanne become a greater, richer nation. I will not hesitate to resort to lesser means if necessary. I am not the Marquis of Loanne to uphold justice.

name: Mikhail
flavor_text: Armor and formal attire is all for show. What I really need is a person I can trust. And that person is you. With you here, even like this, I feel at ease.

name: Mikhail
flavor_text: This sense of trust makes it infinitely better to fight back-to-back rather than have my back against a wall. More than anything, I sense an absolute trust from you when you fight. Leave it to me. I will never betray your trust.
gacha_text: We shall end this fight.

name: Mikhail
flavor_text: I still have a pile of books to read, so go on and play outside. Don't look so sad, Monika. We agreed you would brighten everyone's day with your smile, didn't we?
gacha_text: They are necessary for our survival.

name: Khalid
flavor_text: Tornado? Some might call me that. With Khamsin in hand, I make it rain blood on any battlefield. That's what I do. I'm just a simple mercenary with a simple mission--to get paid.

name: Khalid
flavor_text: Everyone, lend me your strength! With it, I'll call a tornado and we'll smash the enemy in one fell swoop!
gacha_text:
Pass me the reins so that I
may lead us to glorious
victory. Soldiers, will you
follow me into battle?
gacha_serif1: Art thou Khamsin's successor?

name: Khalid
flavor_text: My father always dreamed I would marry a princess one day. With every one of my victories on the battlefield, my father pushed me to get better and better, all for her. I knew, though... that dream would never come true.
gacha_text:
I personally don't have
such ridiculous dreams.
gacha_serif1: But if this is Emelia's dream world, then I'm afraid I have no clue where she is.

name: Khalid
flavor_text: The Kingdom of Naj fell, and the surviving members of the Gessian royal family scattered across the world. I still cannot abandon the hope, however unlikely, that somewhere out there, the princess is alive.

name: Khalid
flavor_text: The true Khamsin is obtained by relinquishing what you hold dearest. That means the Khamsin has become more important to me than anything else. I have no regrets!
gacha_text: I have no regrets!
gacha_serif1: Princess! You're safe...

name: Khalid
flavor_text: You wish to pass through? The toll for Khalid's Gate is costly: your life. If that is too high a price, turn back. If you wish to pass, come closer. I'll collect the toll.
gacha_text: All right, let me take care of them.
gacha_serif1: Blast it! They got ahead of us!

name: Sarah
flavor_text: The Child of Destiny... Desired by none, despised by all, cursed spreader of death and sower of discord, home to misfortune, destroyer of the world... Yes, I am that Child of Destiny.
gacha_text: You need not be afraid.
gacha_serif1: I can feel my life changing. I'm not the person I was yesterday!

name: Sarah
flavor_text: When my big sister isn't around, I sit amongst the flowers and insects. I think about many things. The present... The future... Things I can never tell Sis. Maybe I'm a bad child after all.
gacha_text: Ellen. I'm coming, too.
gacha_serif1: And I'm her sister, Sarah.

name: Sarah
flavor_text: I'm no good with words. I'm awful at saying thank you. I also struggle to comfort others. But surely the trill of my flute will reach the ears of children dejected or in pain.

name: Sarah
flavor_text: What matters isn't physical strength but heart and will. The will to survive, care for others, and yearn for happiness. With hearts as one, we will overcome the power of Oblivion. Come, let us band together.
gacha_text: It is MY responsibility to close the gate.
gacha_serif1: It is MY responsibility to close the gate. Not yours.

name: Sarah
flavor_text: You can't unmake the past or retrieve what's lost. It may be painful to accept, but we still have the future. So, let's believe in the future and open the doors.
gacha_text: Let's believe in the future and open the doors.
gacha_serif1: We're here to rescue you!

name: Sarah
flavor_text: Tom is our leader, and he always looks out for me. I want to grow and contribute as much as I can. So, leave this to me. I'll take out this enemy.
gacha_text: Leave this to me.

name: Ellen
flavor_text: This is my problem. I'll deal with it myself. I don't need any input from you. Got it?
gacha_text:
Well... we used to play house when
we were kids.
gacha_serif1: A lot of things wind up in Loanne. Want to go take a look together? We might as well buy something.
gacha_serif2: But you know, Julian, I don't think I could ever be your lover or anything.

name: Ellen
flavor_text: Everyone tells me I seem like a natural in hand-to-hand combat, but personally, I prefer an axe. There's nothing like the thrill of swinging one around to your heart's content.

name: Ellen
flavor_text: Why do I need to wear THIS just to give some chocolates? I feel so embarrassed...

name: Ellen
flavor_text: Maybe, I got a bit carried away packing. This thing's gonna crush me. The axe? Oh, that's no issue. It's basically a part of me.
gacha_text: Take care, Tom.
gacha_serif1: Ellen, I'd really like to go to Pidona with Tom.
gacha_serif2: What're ya on about? Tom, what's going on here?

name: Ellen
flavor_text: Even if what I see before me is the true form of the Sinistrals, what of it? I will defeat you and close the Abyss Gate. I'll never hand Sarah over to you!
gacha_text: I won't let you die!
gacha_serif1: Sarah... Let's go home.

name: Ellen
flavor_text: It peeves me that I'm seen as some savage woman who waves around an axe all day. A fashionable umbrella suits me just fine, thank you very much.
gacha_text: A fashionable umbrella suits me just fine, thank you very much.
gacha_serif1: If the ancient text Silver found is the real deal, then it's most definitely this island.

name: Ellen
flavor_text: I've stripped away the pointless extras and gone lighter. You're saying I stripped too much? Who told you I meant clothes?! I was talking about my AXE! I was wondering what you were eyeballing. You'll be the first victim of my new axe if you're not careful.

name: Ellen
flavor_text: Julian is stronger when he has nothing holding him back. That's why I'll handle it here. If I told him about this, he'd get carried away, so I'll keep quiet about it.
gacha_text: You go right.

name: Ellen
flavor_text: The strongest punch should have a simple name. Hence, Ellen Punch. And this one's as punchy as it sounds. Wanna give one a try?
gacha_text: Wanna give one a try?

name: Monika
flavor_text: I want to help my brother and Loanne in any way I can. I know my way around a sword. You can count on me.

name: Monika
flavor_text: If there's any information I can provide, I'll tell you gladly. I don't know how much help I'll be, given many places are quite different after these 300 years, but I'll do my best to assist you however possible.
gacha_text:
Can you take my hand?
I don't feel
safe here in the dark.

name: Monika
flavor_text: You've been very good again this year, so I've brought you a present. I can't stay long, though, as I have to hit all the other villages in Loanne as well!
gacha_text:
I've decided! I would like to
bring Christmas joy to less
fortunate children around the world!

name: Monika
flavor_text: Today is the day to celebrate your great deeds. For this occasion, I chose a dress that I hope will convey my deep gratitude to you all.
gacha_text:
May the wind be in
Vanguard's favor.

name: Monika
flavor_text: I rode like the wind that night. It gave me the strength to face my destiny. I feel I will never lose heart, no matter how difficult the daily battles I face, for my heart has sprouted wings and I can fly freely like a bird.
gacha_text: Brother has permitted me to get out and about.
gacha_serif1: So warm.

name: Monika
flavor_text: Despair nearly crushed my heart when we faced Oblivion at the Abyss Gate. Sarah and the Young Boy supported me with the hopes of all creation. I now bear that hope. I can still fight.
gacha_text: But this is NOT one of those times!
gacha_serif1: Sometimes fate calls and you must answer.

name: Monika
flavor_text: The day I left the palace of Loanne and left my brother... The feelings rush back to me. A great unease, but an even greater hope. I shall set out once more. Let's go together.
gacha_text: Now, which way is the port?
gacha_serif1: Julian, I can't stay here... Please, help me escape.
gacha_serif2: Okay...

name: Monika
flavor_text: I want my brother to push me on the swing, even if it's scary because he pushes too hard. I want to ride on the swing with him, too, even if it's scary because he pumps his legs too hard. It's more fun when I'm with my brother!
gacha_text: It's more fun when I'm with my brother!

name: Katarina
flavor_text: Sized me up the moment you saw me, didn't you? Me and my weapon. Well, now I'll show you who I really am. Masquerade!

name: Katarina
flavor_text: There isn't a moment to waste. I will take care of things here. You should go on ahead.
gacha_text:
I will return with the
Masquerade in hand.
gacha_serif1: Lord... Mikhail... I'm so... happy...

name: Katarina
flavor_text: Well, I'm another year older. So while it's not all good news, for now let's celebrate the year to come.
gacha_text:
You should quit while you're
ahead. It's bad luck if you
miss.
gacha_serif1: You don't look like you're in such good shape yourself.

name: Katarina
flavor_text: Everyone probably suspects I cut my hair out of the shame I felt toward Lord Mikhail. But they're wrong. A wild delusion became reality, and I got carried away. I needed to let that go.
gacha_text: You take care as well, Milady.
gacha_serif1: Katarina... What happened to your hair?!

name: Katarina
flavor_text: The Marquis gave me this dagger known as Masquerade. I've concealed it within my dress so that I can stay close to and guard Lady Monika. However, I will need more than a dagger to defend against this foe. It is time to reveal Masquerade's true form.
gacha_text: Please allow me a chance to take back Masquerade.
gacha_serif1: Katarina, do you have the Masquerade on your person?
gacha_serif2: Yes, right here.

name: Katarina
flavor_text: I can't give you my name or discuss my past. Have you heard of any rumors surrounding a special small sword? What of a great sword? Well... do you know of a man who goes about bragging about deceiving women?

name: Katarina
flavor_text: Masquerade, I was a fool. I shouldn't have let go of you. If you will forgive me and fight with me once more, heed my call! Awaken!
gacha_text: If you will forgive me and fight with me once more, heed my call!
gacha_serif1: Alarm!

name: Katarina
flavor_text: It's a great pleasure for me to be able to showcase the Masquerade's true form on such a glorious occasion. The ruffian who gave me this opportunity will be thanked... and judged.
gacha_text: Like the Masquerade, my true form grants me power.

name: Tatyana
flavor_text: So yeah, um, you can call me Santa. And this teddy bear isn't a present, so don't get the wrong idea. If anything, I'm out looking for presents for myself! Got anything for me?

name: Tatyana
flavor_text: Gotcha! Come on, forget studying. Let's go play!

name: Tatyana
flavor_text: Heehee. Come on, take me somewhere. I'm, uh... Eclair. Oh, you've heard that name before? Then call me Bavarois. No, wait, Mille Feuille. Oh, call me anything you like!
gacha_text:
I caught you,
so no running away!
gacha_serif1: Oh! I'm, uh... Eclair.
gacha_serif2: Guess we got no choice. So what's your name?

name: Tatyana
flavor_text: You must think I'm a child who has had an extremely unlucky lot in life. But I've had so much fun visiting all the places in the world. I've not only met all sorts of people, but I'm also lucky enough to have come to a world like this. Where I came from is not important at all.
gacha_text: I wonder who would be the most fun to follow around.
gacha_serif1: No.

name: Tatyana
flavor_text: I don't want treats! I am all the treats! I am Sherbert, Mille Feuille, Candy, Crepe, Souffle, Bavarois, Eclair, and Tarte! Run before I eat you!
gacha_text: I am all the treats!

name: Muse
flavor_text: Holding a grudge over what happened to my father won't do me any good at all. I would rather live alongside others, enjoying every day. Tomorrow will be another good day. I want to go through life always believing this.

name: Muse
flavor_text: I pray for the return of peace and serenity to the world; for the happiness of the people of Pidona; and for the safe return of Charl and his allies. Charl... I pray I can see your warm smile once more.
gacha_text: I pray that you may have a quiet and peaceful life.
gacha_serif1: Look! Lady Muse is awake!

name: Muse
flavor_text: I can't turn around now. I can't let you see me like this. I really want to hug you from behind and keep you here. I want to be with you! But still, I must be strong and see you off. That is my duty.
gacha_text: I can't turn around now. I can't let you see me like this.
gacha_serif1: I can't do this alone... Father... Charl...

name: Charl
flavor_text: The Silver Glove, a relic of the Matriarch, was hidden in a dream world. Am I qualified to inherit such an object? And who am I supposed to protect with it?

name: Charl
flavor_text: I can still use the Shucho Arts without the Silver Glove. But if I collect two of them, I would regain all the abilities I once had.
gacha_text:
...Khalid. I need to borrow the
Silver Glove.
gacha_serif1: The Silver Glove won't disappear!

name: Charl
flavor_text: I am not the Charl I once was. I am now protecting Lady Muse. That is my one and only desire.
gacha_text: It's my turn to lend a hand this time.
gacha_serif1: We will not leave you by yourself.

name: Nora
flavor_text: Whatever the era, being a weaponsmith is all I've ever known, so that's what I'm doing here too. And I can do a lot more now than I could back then. In any case, I just love to bang away!

name: Nora
flavor_text: Hey, this hammer isn't for bashing monsters. It's for forging the greatest weapons and armor there ever were. Aren't there any new weapons or armor out there which may give me inspiration?

name: Nora
flavor_text: Tougher monsters help get the blood flowing for some serious training. Weak opponents don't make you strong. Let's get a real workout today.
gacha_text: We're closed for the day!
gacha_serif1: I can't stay here, Cain. I gotta get even for the old man and find the Spear. Look after the place for me.

name: Nora
flavor_text: I could get coal, but the quality's all over the place. I prefer burning charcoal myself, but it has to be the right size. You see, that's why I have to be so strict.
gacha_text: I want all kinds of weapons.
gacha_serif1: Howdy.
gacha_serif2:
Add to party.
Craft new weapon.
Craft new armor.
Nothing for now.

name: Young Boy
flavor_text: I have forgotten when exactly I learned I was a Child of Destiny. Life was easier once I knew. My whole fate is all preordained, and nothing can change it. I'll just accept what happens until fate sees fit to end me.
gacha_text: Just leave me alone!
gacha_serif1: Just leave me alone!

name: Young Boy
flavor_text: There's a darkness inside me. A darkness that's been growing for a long time. A darkness that is so deep, that it will never disappear under any light. Even so, I will face tomorrow. The light that shines through is warm and soft.
gacha_text: Coming to this world was worth it.
gacha_serif1: We must stop him.

name: Robin
flavor_text: Hahahaha! Know this, evil is always lurking in the dark corners of society! The day has eyes, the night has ears, but Robin the Crusader has both!

name: Robin
flavor_text: The residents of Yarmouth are free. The people there... they smile. All of them. Seeing the joy on their faces gives me the energy to keep doing what I do.

name: Robin
flavor_text: So evildoers do not learn my true identity? So my fans do not hound me while I'm off-duty? No, I just don't want my father to know. That's the only reason.

name: Robin
flavor_text: Titles, medals... No matter what they award me, I can't reveal my true identity. Besides, I'm not doing this for fame. Your wonderful smiles are all I need!
gacha_text:
A hero who fights for
justice doesn't reveal his
identity. That's the rule!

name: Robin (Fake)
flavor_text: Evil stands no chance when Robin the Crusader is around! Why do you look so skeptical? My physique, my graceful moves... and check out this costume! I am the real deal!

name: Robin (Fake)
flavor_text: The Masked Crusader's secrets? They're all right here in my belly! What, you don't believe me? I have many secrets. That's why my belly's so big! Bwahahaha! See ya!
gacha_text:
Hey guys,
can I help?

name: Robin (Fake)
flavor_text: They say my double has been showing up a lot. What I don't get is how he's fooling everyone. I mean, look at me! Who else is this slick? This right here is bona fide Robin Style!

name: Ward
flavor_text: I'm in dire need of income. Will you take me with you on a gig, any gig, so I can make some money? It could be a monster-ridden pit for all I care. No matter the danger, as long as it's profitable, I'm in.

name: Ward
flavor_text: Even if you're poor, you should still mind your appearance. Forget that "it's what inside that counts" nonsense. A man should look sharp--especially if he doesn't have money.
gacha_text:
Do I look like
I have money?
gacha_serif1: You there. How'd you like to make some money?

name: Black
flavor_text: Listen up... If it be treasure, no matter where it be, it exists to be taken by ME. Ye heard me. It's aaall mine. I won't be giving ye bums one coin or one single gem!

name: Black
flavor_text: A famous pirate? Do ye know who stands before ye? The man who faced Forneus, the Abyss Lord of the Sea, twice -- and got his revenge! I be the living legend, Black the Pirate!
gacha_text: No way I'd forget!
gacha_serif1: Yer hair may be longer, but I'd never forget that face. What be this bilge about "Maximus"? Yer name be Jackal!

name: Black
flavor_text: I be used to transformations. So, as requested, I've become a werewolf. It be a full moon tonight. Time to cut loose.
gacha_text: It be a full moon tonight. Time to cut loose.
gacha_serif1: Ye surely suffered a serious shock to've forgotten Black the living legend.

name: Black
flavor_text: Me leg! Me youth! Me strength! They all be back! Slayin' Forneus really does break the curse. I feel the first tears I've ever cried in me life. Black the pirate be back!
gacha_text: Now I've me youth again, I'm unstoppable!
gacha_serif1: Now I've me youth again, I'm unstoppable!

name: Black
flavor_text: I defeated Forneus! The other Sinistrals be weak-willed ninnies. I can do it meself, aye. But ye're itchin' to use that Everfrost Crystal, eh? I'll take ye to Aunus in his Fire Fortress.
gacha_text: Shan't have come on board t' babysit.

name: Herman
flavor_text: That bastard Forneus took everything from me. Me leg, me strength, me treasure, me youth, me friends... I don't care if he be the "Abyss Lord of the Sea", or one of the Sinistrals, or whatever. I'll 'ave me revenge. I won't die until I do!

name: Fullbright XXIII
flavor_text: What helped the Matriarch achieve victory? Ferdinand's bravery? Vassault's wisdom? Nay! It was my ancestor Fullbright XII's economic might. Commerce drives all industries. I fear not Messina nor the Divine Order.
gacha_text: In my line of work, information is the most valuable thing.
gacha_serif1: So you must be Thomas. I'm Fullbright XXIII.

name: Zhi Ling
flavor_text: Spirits of heaven and earth, grant thy blessings today. We shall bestow thy blessing unto thee. Please endow us with what remains. If we break this vow, we offer thee our souls in return. Kindly bestow upon us thy blessings.

name: Zhi Ling
flavor_text: When taking aim at something, never think about what that thing is. Simply empty your mind, and gently loose your arrow. If your mind wavers, your arrow won't find its target.
gacha_text: Stop calling me "Lingling"!
gacha_serif1: You're...

name: Bai Meiniang
flavor_text: Needing help from an old fart like me tells me a lot about you Grave Knights. I do ask a favor in return. Here, I got this knot in my shoulder that just won't go away.
gacha_text:
Whaaat? I just want to
learn about the West.
That's all.
gacha_serif1: That "advisor" Tsao Gao is the one making the decisions. Those people in Huang are a bunch of dirtbags.

name: Boston
flavor_text: Hi, I'm Boston of the lobster tribe from World's End, an island at the edge of the world. At least once in your life, I suggest you come watch the sea flow to the depths beneath the island and feel its indescribable intensity.
gacha_text: Would you mind if I joined you on Vanguard?

name: Boston
flavor_text: These claws are the Lobster Clan's greatest weapon. Obvious, right? They're claws, so they pinch. That's what our enemy expects. And then, all of a sudden, we slam them! Crack open their skulls! That's how these claws are used right.
gacha_text: These claws are the Lobster Clan's greatest weapon.
gacha_serif1: Shenlong Firefist!

name: Boston
flavor_text: I heard it's not the Lunar New Year without some dumplings. So, I sacrificed myself to make these shrimp gyoza. Here, don't be shy, have some! Ha, I'm kidding! Relax, it's only meat. What? You wanted to eat shrimp? Well, I'll cook you first!
gacha_text: We are not cannibals, you know.

name: Boston
flavor_text: World's End vanished with the world's regeneration. Our promised land awaits beyond that new horizon. Now, play some music to commemorate the voyage. And make it lively!
gacha_text: Now, play some music to commemorate the voyage.
gacha_serif1: From the outmost reaches of one world to the innermost reaches of another... Let's clamp down and do this.

name: Faerie
flavor_text: Teehee. I'll shove this spear up evildoers' rears and twist 'til they squeal. Then I'll bash their heads and make 'em froth at the mouth. Come on, evildoers, this is gonna be fun!
gacha_text: I gotta pull a prank on someone.
gacha_serif1: Forgive me for not thanking you earlier. I appreciate you letting me go.

name: Faerie
flavor_text: I am Rocbouquet. Yield to temptation! Come on, swoon already. What? I'm too small to be Rocbouquet? Just cuz I'm a bit little... I worked hard on this! You're so mean!

name: Faerie
flavor_text: Whoa! I can't believe a human made it here. You didn't get lost? Well, since you're here, we'll make sure you enjoy your stay. These memories'll last you a lifetime, hehe.
gacha_text: I can't believe a human made it here. How'd you not get lost?

name: Faerie
flavor_text: We are cute faeries, innocent and pure. We don't understand the concept of crime, so we might do just about anything. We don't mean ill, so please forgive us if we offend you.
gacha_text: We are cute faeries, innocent and pure.
gacha_serif1: I pledge to stand by you as you stood by me.

name: Faerie
flavor_text: That look in your eyes, you're suspecting me. Of course you are, given how you've been treated. But I assure you, it's not poisoned. Now, you've made Faerie say so much, it's your turn to drink up. Let's give everyone a show.
gacha_text: That look in your eyes, you're suspecting me.
gacha_serif1: Were it not for your aid, I would likely have spent the rest of my days in that prison. The green butterfly can be trusted to get you to the Fire Fortress!

name: Rukh
flavor_text: Yes, I am an elephant. This world is filled with monsters. Surely an anthropomorphic elephant isn't that strange. Why do you look at me so? I get it... You've never seen an elephant before, have you? Then take a good look. For an elephant is what I am.

name: Rukh
flavor_text: I heard tales of creatures like Rukh with four legs. Are they like centaurs? They can't be walking on their hands, crawling everywhere. Ridiculous! We have two legs. Two!
gacha_text: Rukh only has and needs two legs.
gacha_serif1: Now that Big Bro's better, guess I'll head out and see the world.

name: Rukh
flavor_text: Elephants are a peaceful race. However, some elephants do fight: the war elephants. Once a war elephant is angered, nothing can stop it. The war elephant is a formidable being.
gacha_text: Fight for yourself and your friends. For the living, it's only natural.

name: Flurry
flavor_text: Who gives out presents on this holy night? A Snowman, of course! You thought it was an old man with a beard? Well, you're wrong. This kind of cold is dangerous for the elderly.

name: Flurry
flavor_text: I am a Snowman. One look at me and that much should be obvious. It is my Everfrost Crystal that prevents me from melting. This ensures you won't wake up to find a puddle of water in my place tomorrow morning.

name: Flurry
flavor_text: I am always serious. I never joke around. I wish people would stop smirking when they see my face. I can't help the way I was born. I wish everyone else were as serious as I am.
gacha_text:
You don't mind if I
take that, right?
gacha_serif1: No touching allowed.

name: Flurry
flavor_text: I don't have to say much. I'm sure you all know what I'm talking about. I'm just going to say one thing.
gacha_text: I will do it!

name: Undine
flavor_text: You seem like you're up to the task, so I have a request, if you'll listen. Of course, I'll give you something in return. Money, or perhaps I can teach you the Genbu Arts, which I'm quite good at. I could teach you other magic as well, if that interests you.

name: Undine
flavor_text: The Genbu Arts control Water Spirits. I myself am a practitioner of Genbu, though I'm not as good as someone like Vassar. He got Vanguard off the ground, after all. One of the characteristics of Genbu is its balance between attack, defense and recovery.

name: Undine
flavor_text: Volcano... That boy is absolutely brimming with talent. It feels as though coming across him was destiny, but I could very well be creating my greatest enemy.
gacha_text:
Oh my, you're all such
cuties. I'm looking
forward to our class.
gacha_serif1: Volcano! Where did you...

name: Undine
flavor_text: You want to move Vanguard? I don't mind helping, but that'll be impossible right now with Volcano around. If only we could get him to leave Mahzoz...
gacha_text: To the south lives a crazed mage named Volcano. Snuff out this firebrand.
gacha_serif1: Hand over the shield!

name: Undine
flavor_text: Water retains no constant shape, instead obeying the form of its vessel. Genbu Mages are no different in their obedience to their leaders. Vassault had no interest in the Sinistrals at first, but he could not ignore the Matriarch's solicitation for help. I have also been led by the Child of Destiny. It was as such 300 years ago, and now is no different.
gacha_text: Your skill... You may be able to help me with a small problem I've been having.
gacha_serif1: Here's 2,000 aurum for your troubles and as an advance. I'm counting on you.

name: Undine
flavor_text: Yes, there are lots of things to do at the beach, but I'm not a child anymore. Relaxing at a Genbu magic-regulated temperature? Now, that's how adults enjoy the beach. Cheers!
gacha_text: Cheers!

name: Leonid
flavor_text: When you've lived as long as I have, eventually everything becomes boring. Except... the rose. The fascinating beauty of its petals, and the cold, hard rejection of its thorns. I never tire of these opposing qualities.

name: Leonid
flavor_text: The Holy Grail. The vessel that held the blood of the Matriarch. I don't know what sort of power was transferred to the Grail along with that blood. But it is my proud duty to protect the Proof of Good Faith that She Herself demonstrated.

name: Leonid
flavor_text: "Leonid, I appoint you Count of Podorui." The Archfiend's words that day yet ring in my ears. 'Twas a rank given by a mere human. It is a shameful memory despite me being second only to the Sinistrals.
gacha_text: I do hope you will make it there alive.
gacha_serif1: Remarkable job in making it here.

name: Leonid
flavor_text: My memories have faded over the long years. It seems I, too, was human once, but I have no such recollection. There are two humans I do remember though: the Matriarch and the Archfiend.
gacha_text:
Impressive! Here is the
chalice in which once
swirled the blood of
the Matriarch.
gacha_serif1: I am Count Leonid of Podorui.

name: Leonid
flavor_text: You judge me evil. And I have no reason to obey you. If you still wish to have my power, offer me blood. Only a pact of blood will prove our mutual trust.
gacha_text: You are not mistaken. And I am that vampire.
gacha_serif1: That look... Do you not fear me?

name: Leonid
flavor_text: Eternity through death or a moment's brilliance in life... But yes, death will make me the one and only. There is no debate.
gacha_text: Being human is not bad.
gacha_serif1: If you are not the god of death, who are you?

name: Maximus
flavor_text: Ah, yes, the Divine Order. A group devoted heart and soul to their teachings. What else could a villain ask for? They question nothing and follow me, Maximus, to the ends of the earth.
gacha_text: People are self-serving. They only believe what they want to believe.

name: Professor
flavor_text: Even if I try to hide it, it still shows: I'm a genius. I can't help but make discoveries, each grander than the last. No one can stop me!

name: Professor
flavor_text: Look at my new invention! Actually, just looking won't do it justice. Let's see what happens when you take a hit from it. You won't die, probably! Trust me, I'm a professor!
gacha_text:
Now hold on just a
nanosecond! I'm more
than just my brains
you know.
gacha_serif1: I'm outta here.
gacha_serif2: You're looking at her. That's right. I'm the Professor. The one and only, at the ripe--Er, tender age of thi... twenty.

name: Professor
flavor_text: Do your worst, waves! With this sailboard, I can do anything. People can't take their eyes off me. Now, all I have to do is sell a bunch of them to fund my next research.
gacha_text: Memories... Shine... Memories... EUREKA!
gacha_serif1: Even a genius like me struggles, you know. Young talent is too much... I mean, I'm only in my twenties.

name: Volcano
flavor_text: The Shucho Arts control Fire Spirits. Aunus, one of the Four Sinistrals, controls fire as well, but he is fire incarnate. His abilities are different from those of a mage. The Shucho Arts emphasize attacking. After all, fire is an intense force. Just like me.

name: Volcano
flavor_text: As thanks for acknowledging my abilities, I'll gladly work with you. The world flourishes on the balance of its spirits. You can't do anything with the Shucho Arts alone. You need other kinds of spells as well.

name: Volcano
flavor_text: There are still so, so many things I don't know about the world. I want to solve these mysteries, and discover the truth. That's why I'm completely involved with absorbing everything I can from Miss Undine right now.
gacha_text: Nice to meet you too, Miss Undine.
gacha_serif1: Air Slash!

name: Volcano
flavor_text: I got her two scoops of ice cream. One red and one blue, her signature colors. But why is she missing? I don't have any spells to keep ice cream from melting!

name: Volcano
flavor_text: The first step is to show a willingness to learn. Let the flame burn in your heart, but learn to control it. The Shucho Arts will respond to two opposing wills. One is the will to burn, the other to control. Okay, you have a go at it now.
gacha_text: Get your spirits fired up! And let's burn!
gacha_serif1: Forgive my overzealous students. I must say, though, you are incredibly talented.

name: Fatima
flavor_text: El Noor. My light, my love. I've always dreamed of the day we'd be reunited. I've waited for so long, with no means to heal your wounds or comfort you. But that all ends today.

name: Fatima
flavor_text: I join now my heart to yours, and engrave upon it the joy of living for tomorrow. I wish to heal your wounds and quench your thirsts. Khalid, you are my light. Now and forever.

name: Fatima
flavor_text: I am allowed to venture out on the night of the festival. I want to see the night market and try exotic stall foods. Most of all, I want to be with you under the lantern lights and look into your eyes. I want to spend this precious time with you.
gacha_text: I told you to stop calling me princess.
gacha_serif1: Princess...
gacha_serif2: But what I admire is your kindness.

name: Fatima
flavor_text: Naj was built on a sea of sand. I could only ever dream of a life like this. I'm so happy now. But when I think of the people of Naj, my heart aches. Should I be living like this?
gacha_text: An actual sea is so much better than one of sand.

name: Gwayne
flavor_text: The day has finally come for me to unleash my full power and raise hell. Those flimsy humans aren't worth it, but if it's against a Sinistral, I shall hold nothing back. I am trembling with joy!
gacha_text: If Byunei thinks the skies are hers to command, she is gravely mistaken.
gacha_serif1: Yet still... if Byunei thinks the skies are hers to command, she is gravely mistaken. Perhaps I will assist you--not for your sake, but for my mother's.

name: Gwayne
flavor_text: The only one to seize and consume this world is I. I shall yield not even the slightest fragment of it to the demons of the Abyss. I shall eradicate all who infringe upon my territory.
gacha_text: All those in my way shall be removed.
gacha_serif1: As a dragon, I must vanquish all who encroach on my skies.

name: Matriarch
flavor_text: To become a ray of hope for the people. That is my destiny. The people have but one wish, which is that the Four Sinistrals be forced back into the Abyss. Allow me to raise a flag to rally the troops. We shall vanquish the Sinistrals!
gacha_text: Allow me to raise a flag to rally the troops. We shall vanquish the Sinistrals!
gacha_serif1: I am the... Child of Destiny.

name: Matriarch
flavor_text: I was hesitant to take on the title of Matriarch, but it's my duty as the Child of Destiny to right the wrongs of the Archfiend. I believe now I must fulfill the Matriarch's mission.
gacha_text: It's my duty as the Child of Destiny to right the wrongs of the Archfiend.

name: Matriarch
flavor_text: It is not I who leads the people. It is their hearts that lead me. I merely walk the path as I am led. Now, let's go together.
gacha_text: Let's go together.
gacha_serif1: Then, I'll make your wish my wish.

name: Matriarch
flavor_text: You are the hero of this battle, Dorra. I am but a witness to your battle with Dragonlord Byunei. Please fight to your heart's content.
gacha_text: Foil the Archfiend's plans!

name: Matriarch
flavor_text: This is the toughest battle I have yet faced. Will I be able to win? I haven't the slightest idea what I should do. Ferdinand, Paulus, Vassault... Somebody, help me!
gacha_text: We have people we'd like to give gifts to as well.
gacha_serif1: Saved the world? My dear, we are not gods. We are but ordinary people.

name: Ottoman
flavor_text: The sword is honest. You must wield it correctly to cut. You must swing it in the right way while dodging the enemy's attacks. This is what I enjoy. The pleasure is all I seek.
gacha_text: Death awaits you if you are within reach of my sword.

name: Ottoman
flavor_text: My left arm moved by itself again. It parried the blow when I wanted to make a counterattack. It's true that the parry made perfect defense, but that would not allow me to create any flow of attack. This left arm is skewing with my swordsmanship.
gacha_text: Don't show me your back.

name: Paulus
flavor_text: Defeat is what I fear most. It's essential I carefully orchestrate my every move going forward. I must calmly observe the Sinistrals and the Matriarch to ascertain who will win in the end.

name: Paulus
flavor_text: The army of Earthlord Alloces, ruler of Pidona. This is where I must prove myself so that I can be promoted to an officer. Now I must distinguish myself from the rest and fulfill my ambitions. It is time to pull out all the stops!
gacha_text: It is time to pull out all the stops!

name: Paulus
flavor_text: Rebels are gathering in Lance. We should strike them before their numbers grow. I say we provoke and unleash beastmen onto them and we shall see how they fare. If they retaliate, our elite force will crush them.
gacha_text: We shall see how they fare.

name: Paulus
flavor_text: To those of you who have fallen to my army, do not grieve for your defeat. There is no shame in losing to Paulus's army. Your wishes will come true one day, and the Sinistrals will be vanquished from this world.
gacha_text: However, I'm using this destiny of yours to move up the ladder.

name: Thorpe
flavor_text: I'm really no good. It's only by the mercy of Young Master that I am able to work for the Fullbright family. I know that everyone says I'm useless. And yet, the Matriarch saw fit to grant me her helm.

name: Thorpe
flavor_text: Even the most fearsome Abyssal demons can't scare me! I have the helm the Matriarch gave me. I'll take the lead. Charge!
gacha_text: Let's go!

name: Vassault
flavor_text: The Sinistrals are uncoordinated. If we strike at each of their individual weaknesses, victory will be ours. Why, then, have we been unable to accomplish this? It is because we are equally unorganized and quarreling.

name: Vassault
flavor_text: The Sinistrals? Not interested. My only wish is to devote my wholehearted attention to the Genbu Arts. The Sinistrals never stood in my way, and I have neither the time nor energy to give them any consideration.
gacha_text: I seek to master Genbu Arts. Leave me be.

name: Vassault
flavor_text: What follows the first victory is key. Some get carried away and try to press on, but we should never do so. We must anticipate the enemy's counterattack and reap the fruits of victory.
gacha_text: We must anticipate the enemy's counterattack and reap the fruits of victory.

name: Vassault
flavor_text: The arts of the five elements complement and control each other, creating a cycle in the world. Following this logic, it is possible to create a new magic. A mage needs not a spark of inspiration but the patience to pursue the truth.
gacha_text: A mage needs not a spark of inspiration but the patience to pursue the truth.

name: Ferdinand
flavor_text: Until the Matriarch and Dorra bring an end to Byunei, we must do our best to draw the attention of as many enemies as possible and defeat them. Now go wreak havoc upon their ranks, and bring the mightiest of adversaries back to me!

name: Ferdinand
flavor_text: I only wanted to settle the frontier. But the Matriarch bestowed upon me the ridiculous title of Marquis of Loanne. I never suspected I'd become a true nobleman. I imagine the one most surprised by this development would be that astronomer.
gacha_text: I do what I must. I will not hesitate to give it my all. That's all there is to it.

name: Ferdinand
flavor_text: Call me a wild boar warrior, a face-first charging fool, whatever you want. I'll be the first one to storm the walls. I'm making things difficult for you as your commander, you say? Well, keep up then!
gacha_text: No, there are still those I must protect. I will not give in that easily!
gacha_serif1: No, there are still those I must protect. I will not give in that easily!

name: Ferdinand
flavor_text: Halt! This is as far as you go. I can't allow the likes of you to see the Matriarch. I'm responsible that you got this far. Your fight is with me!
gacha_text: Feeling ashamed of your old self is a sign of progress.
gacha_serif1: Good. Let's show the town what we're made of.

name: Hilda
flavor_text: Stop calling me a lady. My family was only fortunate enough to be less affected by the Rise of Morastrum. I could've been on the opposite side of Ferdinand. So it's only natural that we should work together to overcome the calamity.

name: Hilda
flavor_text: Let me handle the enemies that try to get behind us. You concentrate on defeating the mighty foe ahead. I know you can do it, Ferdinand. You've never let me down.
gacha_text: I'll round up everyone then. We'll need Justerm's volunteer army flag, too.
gacha_serif1: Of course. I'd be worried sick if you go alone.

name: Hilda
flavor_text: There are those who disapprove of a lady cooking by herself, but not me. I don't even think you have to be that skilled, especially when you're doing it for others. I believe your passion will reach them.
gacha_text: We must gather ingredients first.
gacha_serif1: Is this not the first time we meet? Do you know me from somewhere?

name: Ludwig
flavor_text: The Marquis of Loanne suppressed the rebellion. And he had help from the mercenary known as the Tornado. I'm glad to hear that you're alive and well, Khalid... I need you to accomplish much more.
gacha_text: I use what I can in this restless world.

name: Fullbright XII
flavor_text: Profit comes first for a merchant. Helping others brings me profit. That is the only reason I do it. Wars are profitable, but there is much more money to be made in a world at peace. That's all. I am not working for some ideal.

name: Nacht Zweiger
flavor_text: The barrier holding me back's been broken! An inexplicable power now sits behind my wheel. I'm going for a good drive, and there's not a soul who can stop me!
gacha_text: An inexplicable power now sits behind my wheel.

name: Nacht Zweiger
flavor_text: I'm about to run the best race ever. I don't care what it's for, who I'm racing, or where. I just want to go as fast as I can. That's all I need to know joy.
gacha_text: I just want to go as fast as I can. That's all I need to know joy.

name: Kyrdlund's Mayor
flavor_text: Yes, I am the mayor. What can I do for you? Oh, it's you. Yeees, I remember you. As I recall, you're the one who went to Zweig to help me run an errand, aren't you? No? Then, you must be the one who ran the errand to Podorui. What? Wrong again?

name: Kyrdlund's Mayor
flavor_text: A monster's taken residence near town. We must offer a sacrifice. If only an adventurer would come and defeat it. Well, I suppose that's of no consequence to you cute mice.
gacha_text: I'm sorry, did you say something?
gacha_serif1: I'm the mayor of this town.

name: Asura
flavor_text: There are many humans who seem to mistake me for a dojo master, but that is not the case. Some people have indeed grasped a plethora of skills from fighting me, though that is not why I myself fight!

name: Asura
flavor_text: No one came for me. All because I shouted that I was no dojo master. I miss the days when adventurers would beat me over and over again. Fight me! Beat me again and again and become stronger, seekers!
gacha_text: Become stronger, seekers!

name: Dorra
flavor_text: Look up at the sky. Fear the creatures that roam the world beyond your reach. Fear the power that takes all your treasure and devours your livestock. Fear the flames that raze everything to the ground. Fear the sudden, winged death. Fear the dragons!
gacha_text: We dragons are of tooth and claw.
gacha_serif1: Tigers are creatures of endurance, but we dragons are of tooth and claw.

name: Bunnie
flavor_text: I will never forget you.
gacha_text: I will never forget you.

name: Bunnie
flavor_text: When I awoke I'd been turned into a human! A female one at that! I bet the Professor did this. She promised not to experiment on me anymore! What sort of experiment is Halloween?
gacha_text:
Hehe, now that's a
transformation!
gacha_serif1: Hehe! Now that's a transformation!

name: Bunnie
flavor_text: Do da tssh, do da tssh, bum, ba dum. Do da tssh, do da tssh, bum, ba dum. I've got rhythm in my blood. No need to rush it. Do da tssh, do da tssh, bum, ba dum.

name: Alloces
flavor_text: Those who fight are warriors. In battle, they seek victory. It is what proves their worth. Now, triumph over me. Shed blood, sweat, and tears for me!
gacha_text: Challenge me.
gacha_serif1: Bleed for me!

name: Alloces
flavor_text: I need not the title of the Sinistral if it means sitting complacently in a palace. I take pride as a warrior who fights the strongest enemy on the front lines.
gacha_text: You shall beg for mercy that will never come!

name: Byunei
flavor_text: Having passed through the gate from the dark depths of the Abyss, Byunei, Lord of the Dragons, has descended. My triad will shred your flesh. Trinity Blaster!
gacha_text: Pitiful maggots.

name: Byunei
flavor_text: You can come riding in on Gwayne, Dorra, or any other dragon. But you will be nothing more than a maggot. Crawl on the ground like the maggots you are!

name: Byunei
flavor_text: The Abyss also has a sky, stagnant and neither day nor night. I have always ruled that sky, where the Sinistrals endlessly fight. But this world's sky is ever-changing, and I have no intention of letting go of this delight.
gacha_text: Foul worms! How many times... will you trespass on my domain?! Feel my wrath!

name: Byunei
flavor_text: Plenty of fools tried to challenge me in the Abyss. You shall understand your folly the second I rip you apart. You shall be dead before I finish my move!
gacha_text: Number matters not. You're still nothing but worthless insects.

name: Byunei
flavor_text: Imp, Byrd, Hound. I've got just the right plaything for you. Go and have fun. I shall nap a bit longer, for I was having the most pleasant dream.
gacha_text: Looks like an insect to me.

name: Byunei
flavor_text: That's why I'm so obsessed with this sky. You never feel such air in the stagnant sky of the Abyss. My skin is delighted. I finally know what it means to feel refreshed, and I'll never let go of it.
gacha_text: It's refreshing.

name: Aunus
flavor_text: 'Tis your fate to die. There is no escaping it. Accept it with grace. In return, I shall grant you a wish. To have your dream come true before you die or to die with your wish unfulfilled: seems like an easy decision to me.

name: Aunus
flavor_text: There was one burdened with the Morastrum, yet resisted their fate with death. But you are different. You do not have the power to resist. So accept your fate! You will suffer otherwise.
gacha_text: Accept your fate!
gacha_serif1: ...'Tis fate.

name: Aunus
flavor_text: How unfortunate are the flames of the Abyss, having nothing to burn! The flames of this world are lucky. They can burn anything! Some are pleased with the flames, yet others grieve. Now, what should I see go up in flames next?
gacha_text: Burn it all.

name: Aunus
flavor_text: Look into the flame vortex. Do not look away, and keep your focus. Your mind is now caught in this flame vortex. There is no escape. Remain until it consumes you.
gacha_text: Your end is inevitable!

name: Forneus
flavor_text: Foolish humans... calling their pathetic little boats "warships" and fighting for rule over the ocean. You are merely crawling upon its surface. The true ocean spreads far below.

name: Forneus
flavor_text: I invite you to my Undersea Palace, foolish humans. There are beautiful creatures, wonderful food, and fabulous treasures beyond imagination waiting for you. I, Forneus, Lord of the Sea, shall welcome you.
gacha_text: Taste the power of the Abyss!
gacha_serif1: Taste the power of the Abyss!

name: Forneus
flavor_text: The sea in the Abyss is deep and fathomless, a mere nothingness. The sea of this world is small and dreadfully crowded, but how lively it is! I intend to explore the pleasures of this boisterous sea for now.
gacha_text: Taste the power of the Abyss!

name: Forneus
flavor_text: Who said every journey must begin in a town? The world has many faces. A journey that starts and ends in the sea is just as valid. The choice is yours. Do not disappoint me.
gacha_text: Do not disappoint me.

name: Mugplant
flavor_text: Blep-blop! Mlem-mlem! Bleh-bloop! You laughed! That means you lost. Time to eat!
gacha_text: You laughed! That means you lost.

name: Blue
flavor_text: I left my hometown to study magic, a journey that continues to this day. With you, I might learn even more about spells. Why don't we travel together?

name: Blue
flavor_text: I have a twin. What was meant for one person was split two ways. Only one of us can become a perfect mage. And that one will be me.
gacha_text:
Who am I?
Blue?
Rouge?

name: Blue
flavor_text: The world's full of red things. I can't stand it! Red clothes and hair, especially. Red things on people are vile. And red-related names? Those are just the worst!

name: Blue
flavor_text: I've been on a long journey to kill Rouge. It all ends here. Once I kill him, I'll become a complete mage again and finally be able to return to the Magic Realm.
gacha_text: Once I kill him, I'll be a complete mage.
gacha_serif1: You can learn more about Arcane and Rune Magic in Devin. Hurry or you won't be able to acquire the spells Rouge has learned!

name: Blue
flavor_text: This is no illusion. This dragon is a manifestation of my magic. As long as I harness my powers, I'll be able to make the dragon dance. But it is not easy. The spell will try to consume the caster at any moment. Now, dance!
gacha_text: Now, dance!

name: Blue
flavor_text: I hear this area has long been a place where philosophy flourished. It may hold the key to a new spell. A simple stroll has now become an adventure in itself. It seems that coming here was a good choice.
gacha_text: No spell is born where there is no human activity.

name: Riki
flavor_text: Margmel's a region of monsters. Riki is a creature called a Lummox. To save Margmel from impending doom, Riki's on a journey to gather rings that grant wishes.

name: Riki
flavor_text: I need to gather all the rings to save Margmel. You'll help me, right? Right? Right right right right right?

name: Riki
flavor_text: This is how Margmel really was. Such a beautiful place with a wonderful aroma and the gentlest of breezes. Yep! Margmel truly was a wonderful world!
gacha_text: Return to your former glory, Margmel!
gacha_serif1: Grandma... So this is the Margmel you told me about.

name: Riki
flavor_text: Look! Look! Look! That fish is flying! Or is it a monster? It's so shiny and pretty, though! Let's go have a look. We could swim and fly together. Wagh! Did I know how to swim?
gacha_text: We could swim and fly together.

name: T260G
flavor_text: I'm in the field fighting on Captain Thyme's orders. Where has he gone? I cannot function without orders.

name: T260G
flavor_text: Captain Thyme, I'm afraid I cannot assist you in your search for parts. This arm has a delicate piece that cannot risk being broken. No, Miss Rose, I am not being lazy.
gacha_text: Yes, Captain Thyme.
gacha_serif1: Mobility err-or. Attack err-or.
gacha_serif2: This ungrateful bucket of bolts. I get him working again, and all he can say is "Err-or, err-or."

name: T260G
flavor_text: Mission: Enter Gatalympics and win gold. Probability of victory in Tarzan jump: 99.99%. Probability of sinking when landing on mudflat: 100%. Captain, what should I do?
gacha_text: Mud and salt cause catastrophic failure for mechs.

name: T260G
flavor_text: My last mission is to disable the region buster. Must enter the program's core. Must destroy it without triggering the self-destruct protocol which will affect many regions.
gacha_text: Omega body: Charging energy.
gacha_serif1: Cosmic Rave

name: T260G
flavor_text: V-MAX requires cooldown following activation. As such, this system should be used when victory is assured. Affirmative, the V is for Victory. And the time for victory is now.
gacha_text: Attack!!
gacha_serif1: V-MAX

name: Alkaiser
flavor_text: Evil has nowhere to run when THIS superhero is around! A flash of lightning and... Alkaiser Change! Now taste defeat! Al-Phoenix! No one can know my true identity... The transforming hero, Alkaiser, is on the scene!
gacha_text:
I know, Hawk.
We both have a lot
we can't talk about.
gacha_serif1: What's the matter, Hawk?

name: Red
flavor_text: I do have an ace up my sleeve, but I'm not showing you that just yet. I don't need it anyway. Evildoers everywhere, you are going down!

name: Red
flavor_text: Paying your respects at the shrine at the start of a new year is important. For your family's benefit, for Alkaiser's benefit and of course for that cutie in your life! This year, I'm gonna make all my dreams come true!

name: Alkaiser
flavor_text: Dammit. I feel their hits in my bones. Can't see straight... But it is at these times when true heroes rise to the fore. Behold my ultimate attack! Re-Al-Phoenix!
gacha_text: I'll never forgive Black X!
gacha_serif1: Re-Al-Phoenix

name: Alkaiser
flavor_text: "Evildoers will taste the fist of justice!" How's this pose? Nobody would dare do anything bad when they see my poster. It's important work to uphold day-to-day safety and security in the local community.
gacha_text: It's time to morph into Alkaiser!
gacha_serif1: You shameless scum!! Threatening a defenseless child.

name: Red
flavor_text: The name's Red Okonogi. What? It's lame? Red's my favorite color, the color of my blazing heart. No, it's not a pun. Hey, where are you going? I'm not done talking!

name: Alkaiser
flavor_text: You got the same power as a hero, you say? Well, let me tell you. The power of a hero is the power of justice. And that comes from the heart, something you Black X fiends will never have!
gacha_text: ...your powers for good.
gacha_serif1: You could have used...

name: Emelia
flavor_text: My hopes, my dreams, my ideals, my fiance... You took everything from me. I will never forgive you! Now, show yourself, so I can send you to hell where you belong!
gacha_text: Unforgivable...!
gacha_serif1: Joker...

name: Emelia
flavor_text: Just a regular battle outfit this time. My usual role is supporting Annie, Lyza, or Roufas with Suppressing Fire. I'm not a Gladius cosplayer or anything weird like that.
gacha_text: I won't forget you.
gacha_serif1: What a nice view... Such clear skies... I feel like I could forget all about Joker...

name: Emelia
flavor_text: Those legendary soldiers who could make it back safely from a battlefield or mission, no matter how difficult, without breaking a sweat... I am like them now. By sharpening my senses and my mind, I can keep my cool at all times when on a mission.
gacha_text: I seem to be a pretty good shot.
gacha_serif1: Oh, so this is a pistol! I've never shot one before!

name: Emelia
flavor_text: Today, my job is to enjoy this footbath and some onsen manju while wearing a yukata. Isn't it grand? If you were expecting to see me getting into an onsen, too bad for you. I have to be selective about the jobs I take, as he's been very fussy lately. But I do love a jealous man.
gacha_text: My feet get so cold. A good footbath is pure bliss.

name: Pink Tiger
flavor_text: Can I jump this high, you ask? I'm Pink Tiger! There's not a move I can't do! I can spin from here and plunge my heel right into his head! Uh, maybe that's a bit much, but I will land on his head and show everyone how it's done!
gacha_text: Adjusting to the situation is the mission of a pro.
gacha_serif1: No need to do as we do. We're counting on your dual-wielding technique!

name: Emelia
flavor_text: I know Koorong's alleys like the back of my hand. It's a dead end up ahead and you can't escape into the sewers. You won't get away. Not this time!
gacha_text: You won't get away. Not this time!

name: Asellus
flavor_text: I always wondered who I really was. Was I human? Mystic? Neither? But I had no need to wonder. I am Asellus. And that's all I need to know.
gacha_serif1: And so I continue to live with this destiny. That's all I wanted to say.

name: Asellus
flavor_text: To be honest with you, I was perplexed as to why I had to receive chocolates. But I couldn't very well let your sincerity go unanswered, could I? So, please help yourself to one of these.
gacha_text:
This world is so wonderful...
and so free...
gacha_serif1: Have you seen Princess White Rose?

name: Asellus
flavor_text: This is an important ritual to free an imprisoned soul. And it's the only way. Compose yourself, Asellus. Clear your mind and just fight. You're a mystic, you can do this.
gacha_text:
I've learned that it's alright
to like myself just the way
I am.
gacha_serif1: And so I continue to live with this destiny. That's all I wanted to say.

name: Asellus
flavor_text: Does the festival get my blue mystic blood pumping, or my red human blood? Either way, when I march through town with those enormous hikiyama festival floats, all my worries fade.
gacha_text:
Enya, enya!
Yoisa, yoisa!

name: Asellus
flavor_text: What color is your blood? If it's red, can I have some? Wait! I was doing my vampire lines. I don't REALLY want red blood. I swear.

name: Asellus
flavor_text: The old ways will be thrown away and a new history of the Mystics will be written. I will renew this castle and all of Facinaturu. Mystics with power, come to me. Ranks are no more. I welcome all kinds of powers, be it mystic power, strength, or charm.
gacha_text: I must teach him who is really in control.
gacha_serif1: I am beyond him in every respect.

name: Asellus
flavor_text: The tiger is a symbol of great progress. So, is it progress that awaits me? Will it bring happiness? Now that I'm a half-mystic, I wonder what kind of progress could await me beyond that.
gacha_text: Happiness awaits in the future. That's what I believe.

name: Asellus
flavor_text: To be honest, I'm tired of always being asked to wear men's clothes. But White Rose's costumes are always amazing. They're cute, beautiful, and she matches them so well with the roses on her head. I wonder what she looks like today.
gacha_text: Because you're really special to me, White Rose.
gacha_serif1: Could I be like the knight who rescued the princess? Could I have the strength to save those I love?

name: Lute
flavor_text: It's a crazy world we're livin' in. And me worryin' wouldn't do a thing. Sometimes you just gotta wait these things out, you know? Let's just take it easy.
gacha_text: Yo, cutie, how you doin'?
gacha_serif1: Well, I'll be going now.

name: Lute
flavor_text: Doo doo doo, dee dee dee, da da da, la la la, fee fee feee, day da day da daaa, la dee doo da day...

name: Lute
flavor_text: Forget your sorrow. All you need is fun, alright~ Forget tomorrow. Don't care if I die tonight~ Let's dance. Sing with me~ I'm alive, and I'm with you~
gacha_text: Let's dance. Sing with me~

name: Fuse
flavor_text: IRPO brings in tons of agents from various regions, so we are a motley crew. But there can only be one Number 1. Do you know who that is? That's right, the very man standing before you now!
gacha_text: Leave it to me.
gacha_serif1: I'm going to rip away Campbell's facade.

name: Fuse
flavor_text: You get what I'm sayin', right? I know you're no fool, though. Is someone picking you up from the air? Or is there some other trick you're hiding up there?
gacha_text: I know you're no fool, though.
gacha_serif1: Show yourself, Joker!

name: Ren
flavor_text: Emelia, you are my everything. Nothing in this region is more precious to me. I'll even resign as an IRPO officer if you want. I have eyes only for you, and I want you to look only at me.

name: Ren
flavor_text: Isn't he just great? Why, you say? Well, he's a flop with the ladies. Probably because he goes over the top on everything. He's also a chatterbox, which girls hate. I probably shouldn't tell him about Emelia.
gacha_text: Probably because he goes over the top on everything.
gacha_serif1: When's the next time you can take a vacation?
gacha_serif2: I don't think I'll be getting a vacation.

name: Joker
flavor_text: You thought you had me, huh? Well, I'm always on top. Stupid patrol... Working yourself to the bone for a pittance, feeling accomplished when you catch some little crooks... Pathetic, isn't it?
gacha_text: I'm always on top.
gacha_serif1: An emergency at Trinity Base? Must be the end of the world.

name: Silence
flavor_text:
Silence's notes:
I might have things to say, but I can guess the person's reply and the result of the conversation. And since that's how it is, there's no need to say anything. Excessive talking is not a virtue.

name: Doll
flavor_text: What's my relationship with Fuse? What do you mean by that? I am a member of the IRPO and so is Fuse. That's it. Fuse is talented, but he doesn't know how to plan ahead. What's important is to get the desired results with the least amount of input and to have a Plan B.
gacha_text: Name's Doll. I'm an IRPO officer.
gacha_serif1: Now's your only chance to laugh.

name: Doll
flavor_text: I never mentioned it? I've played the violin since I was five. I even take to the stage in my off time. Spare me your shock if you value your life.
gacha_text: The violin can be quite loud.

name: Rabbit (SF1)
flavor_text: I don't know much about all the different types of rabbits, so I don't know if I actually look like a rabbit or not. In any case, my code name is just used for identification purposes, so it doesn't matter what I'm called. I do quite like this name, though.

name: Rabbit (SF1)
flavor_text: My functions are not only recon, comms, and jamming. I'm also equipped for battle. Otherwise, I wouldn't be able to carry out my IRPO missions. But of course, my role is a supporter, so the lead should decide what I do.
gacha_text: If the case is solved, good.
gacha_serif1: Searching for Metal Black Base.
gacha_serif2: Then, come with us!

name: Cotton
flavor_text: Myu myu? Myu myu kyu kyu kyu kyu! Myu myu myu myu myu myu kyu kyu kyu kyu kyu kyu myu myu myu kyu kyu kyu kyu myu myu myu myu myu myu myu!
gacha_text: Kyu kyu kyu kyu kyu kyu kyu kyu!
gacha_serif1: Hey, Cotton!

name: Roufas
flavor_text: What it means to be top brass is that you don't have to get your hands dirty to get things done. Don't assume that I'll save you when you get into trouble. If you understand that, then get to work.
gacha_text: We are the secret organization Gladius.
gacha_serif1: There must be an organization to do all the things IRPO can't.

name: Annie
flavor_text: You must really have a death wish if you're starting a fight with me. Well, people are into all sorts of things, so I'll indulge you. Prepare to get hurt.

name: Annie
flavor_text: Hey, what's gonna happen? Is it gonna be dangerous? Good! Life's no fun without a little danger.
gacha_text:
From here on out
you're a volunteer.
gacha_serif1: Hey, keep your distance!

name: Annie
flavor_text: I'm Annie, captain of the Gladius Bandwagon. Launching headfirst into danger? That's what I do. But only because I know Lyza, Roufas, and Emelia have my back.

name: Annie
flavor_text: Our work is mostly gathering intel. But with the exception of assassinations, we do everything. We do our best to abide by the law, but when things get dicey, the job comes first. We are not heroes by any stretch of the imagination, but neither are we villains.
gacha_text: Doing things the right way means nothing if you're dead.
gacha_serif1: Are you also interested in matters concerning the Cube?
gacha_serif2: Not really. I don't really care all that much.

name: Annie
flavor_text: Your sniper rifle, with its long range and accuracy, has been set up in a place with no blind spots. And you, the person behind the scope, never miss a shot. You are the epitome of perfection. But, unfortunately for you, I've already gotten through your defenses!
gacha_text: Don't just call out to me like that. Things could get bloody.
gacha_serif1: I'm Annie. This has happened 3, 4, 5... or maybe 6 times already.

name: Annie
flavor_text: Thanks for always workin' hard. Don't worry, I'm paying you. You're young. Between food and dates, you can't have too much money. By the way, you don't have to ask me out. I'm good.
gacha_text: Business is business.
gacha_serif1: Let me have some dessert first.
gacha_serif2: Now, tell me about the base.

name: Lyza
flavor_text: Whatever you need, I can help. Legal, illegal... what sort of services do you require? I promise you we won't let you down.

name: Lyza
flavor_text: You let your guard down because I don't use weapons. But these fists and feet are all the weapons I need. Care for more?

name: Lyza
flavor_text: You won't get paid more for taking longer, so it's better to get it done quickly. That said, don't get sloppy, and stay alert. It's a simple job. We do it clean. We do it fast.

name: Lyza
flavor_text: Perhaps you're thinking, "Someone would actually arrange a meet up in a dark alley like this?" Even if I am waiting for someone, it's not you. Besides, with your ugly mug, I don't think there'd be anyone willing to wait for you.
gacha_text: Perhaps you're thinking, "Someone would actually arrange a meet up in a dark alley like this?"
gacha_serif1: Ok, I'll try that. You're so kind.
gacha_serif2: But people often say I'm a cold-hearted woman.

name: Lyza
flavor_text: Look at the time. I don't want to miss the sunset, so let's find a place where we can have a drink wearing this. Sorry, what? You're joking, right? No way... You wanna be top brass that badly?!
gacha_text: I don't like people who only think about themselves.
gacha_serif1: Where there's people, there's intel. Be patient.

name: M Black
flavor_text: I may be one of the top brass in Black X, but I am alone. I care not for their schemes or who is the strongest. I'm simply waiting to fight that man. Solitude is ideal.
gacha_text: I request a duel.
gacha_serif1: You destroyed my facility. Remarkable.

name: M Black III
flavor_text: Dr. Klein gave me this body. He made it after exhaustive research on your moves and attack patterns. With this body and my samurai spirit, I will surpass you. Let us fight, Alkaiser!
gacha_text: But I can't very well claim victory by defeating an exhausted hero.
gacha_serif1: A new and improved M Black knows all your moves and attack patterns. It will defeat you without a problem.
gacha_serif2: It's time to put up or shut up. Get ready to face death, Alkaiser.

name: M Black
flavor_text: Someone strong enough to destroy our base... I've waited for the day when such a powerful man would appear. A blow to Black X, but a joy to me. Now, we fight!
gacha_text: I'm always up for a serious fight.
gacha_serif1: Wait, youngster. Aren't you interested in Black X?

name: Rouge
flavor_text: I am Rouge. I'm on the trail of a mage called Blue. What will I do when I find him, you ask? Defeat him. That's all there is to it.

name: Rouge
flavor_text: I'm not strong enough yet. Without more power, I cannot face my other half. Hey you, do you know of a place where I can acquire power?

name: Rouge
flavor_text: I may look like a man, but in fact I'm only half of one. I am indeed half a person. And when I obtain my other half, that day will be the true day of my birth.
gacha_text:
I'm traveling the world in order
to study magic.
gacha_serif1: I am the Realm sorcerer, Rouge. I travel the world to master skills and spells.

name: Rouge
flavor_text: My entire life has led to this day. I'd nearly given up, but I recalled that figure looming over me and I was able to rise again. Blue, I'll thank you for that... Once I kill you.
gacha_text: My entire life has led to this day.
gacha_serif1: I can't return to the Realm. Not yet. This is where we go our separate ways.

name: Rouge
flavor_text: The Magic Realm's most powerful mage is tasked with holding back hell. It seems that hell has appeared in this world as well. Now, let's see what the most powerful mage can do.
gacha_text: Now, let's see what the most powerful mage can do.
gacha_serif1: Can I reach hell from here?

name: Rouge
flavor_text: When you think of adventure, you might expect it to be fun, but life is not so kind. Danger lurks in every corner. Knowing that, would you still go? If so, I will join you.
gacha_text: People can always move forward.
gacha_serif1: JP raised!

name: Gen
flavor_text: Hey. Name's Gen. Take a seat. Go on. Take a load off. Don't worry, everything works out in the end.

name: Gen
flavor_text: I spent all my time in Wakatu learning how to use a sword. In the end, I could wield it like it was an extension of my body. But none of my training made any difference against Trinity's weapons, and Wakatu was destroyed.

name: Gen
flavor_text: I'm here to show you clowns a real warrior. Is Asura in charge around here? Or is it that lobster? Not important, now that I'm here. Let's start things off by you getting me a drink.
gacha_text: Close your eyes. Use your ears.
gacha_serif1: This is the Chamber of the Bladewraith.

name: Gen
flavor_text: Guns beat swords. It's as clear as rock beating scissors and water beating fire. Why are you hesitating? Relax. Even the best swordsman can't beat a gun. I'm ready. Come on, pull the trigger.
gacha_text: Wanna try it...?
gacha_serif1: ...Are you Gen?
gacha_serif2: Huh? Lookin' for somethin', bud?

name: Gen
flavor_text: Hooray. I'm glad I don't get any strange looks for drinking during the day here. Not that I've ever cared what people think. Let's have a good time. First one to have fun wins!
gacha_text: Let's have a good time. First one to have fun wins!

name: Mei-ling
flavor_text: When I say rings, I don't mean the engagement kind. There are some powerful rings in this world. I don't know who made them, but I know they're out there.

name: Mei-ling
flavor_text: A bright moon lights up the night, yet I'm alone. A special time to spend with someone at your side. I feel ever the more lonely. What about you? Are you alone? Perhaps this is the cost of ambition.
gacha_text: What a coincidence. I'm looking for rings, too. Where have you come from?
gacha_serif1: You sure know a lot about the rings.
