gacha_serif2: It's because I'm currently studying the rings. Riki, what's up with that ring?

name: Mei-ling
flavor_text: Oh? I thought you couldn't handle the heat. Is it just with hot food? Are you waiting for someone, too? This is the perfect place to pass the time. Speaking of time, he's late.
gacha_text: I thought you couldn't handle the heat.

name: Fei-on
flavor_text: I have so much more training to undergo. Yet, it is undeniable that real battle is a superior form of training, so come at me, and do not stop. My training has only just begun.
gacha_text: I keep my hair like this for my training.
gacha_serif1: I was eaten by Tanzer, that's why...
gacha_serif2: You never change... Making me wait because you have to train.

name: Zozma
flavor_text: We Mystics are always bored. See, every day is forever the same. But me? I love a good time. I thank you for keeping me entertained, but I've had enough now. We're done.
gacha_text: We Mystics are always bored.
gacha_serif1: Sorry I didn't properly introduce myself last time. I'm Zozma. You're Asellus, right?

name: Zozma
flavor_text: I understand why Humans long for and rely on the power of Mystics. That's the weakness of Humans. But you should know that Mystics will never lend their power for nothing. You will always pay a price.
gacha_text: To think I'd end up helping humans.

name: Ildon
flavor_text: Aesthetics. That is what separates Mystics from humans. Without beauty, you're not a Mystic. As a knight, undying loyalty to my Lord is my aesthetic. My loyalty does not waver.

name: Ildon
flavor_text: I will train her in the most basic of Mystic abilities. That's all I've been ordered to do by my Lord. But why do you favor this half-Mystic, Rastaban? Oh, fine. This is your request. It shall be done.
gacha_text: I was asked by Rastaban to protect you.
gacha_serif1: Relax, I am not here to take you back to Facinaturu. I was asked by Rastaban to protect you.

name: Ildon
flavor_text: Surprised? It seems you didn't think a mystic would don such an outfit. Well, our sense of style far surpasses that of humans. Whatever the clothes, we wear them better.
gacha_text: Whatever the clothes, we wear them better.

name: Ciato
flavor_text: Allow me to perform a sword dance. The blade moves and guides my body flowingly. In that simplicity, I suggest the graceful motions of a puissant, ferocious tiger.
gacha_text: Allow me to perform a sword dance.

name: Ciato
flavor_text: I am well aware of my critics. It would seem some cannot stand the fact that I serve the Charm Lord with all my heart. Neither do I care. None can know my heart of hearts.

name: Princess Rei
flavor_text: Even Orlouge will find it hard to follow me to this world. His persistence is vexing. Does he not realize the chased will run? Lord of Temptation? An ill-fitting name.

name: Princess Rei
flavor_text: Did you think this is some sort of game? With power comes sacrifice, but a Mystic's power knows no bounds. That is why humans should not use it lightly.
gacha_text: What business do you have with me?
gacha_serif1: It's sold out.

name: Princess Rei
flavor_text: Some pray quietly. Some ring bells and sing. Each person has their own way of devoting their heart to something. It's a noble pursuit to cleanse the heart and soul before the new year. It is not a day to ask for gifts.
gacha_text: It's a noble pursuit to cleanse the heart and soul before the new year.

name: Princess Rei
flavor_text: Everyone, come outside. Let us see the new year's sunrise. I cannot say how many times I have seen this sight, yet the first day of the year is always special. It never fails to renew my heart.
gacha_text: Let us see the new year's sunrise.

name: Princess Lion
flavor_text: We both fight for the one we love. Neither victory nor defeat will make us waver in our undying devotion to the wonders of love. Is there anything more important than this to those who were born to love? Now, let us settle this with a fight!
gacha_text: I shall defeat you with all that I am!
gacha_serif1: I'm only after one person, and it's not you.
gacha_serif2: The time for words is over. Let's settle this with a fight.

name: Princess Lion
flavor_text: My heart yearns for a love it cannot come close to fulfilling. The more I pursue my dreams, the further out of reach it becomes. It is precisely because I cannot convey my feelings that they are all the more precious. Hanging on to these emotions to the very end satisfies both my mind and my body.
gacha_text: The only one who has yet to succumb to this sword is Lord Orlouge.
gacha_serif1: I am your opponent!
gacha_serif2: Hmph! The only one to have never succumbed to the might of my sword is Lord Orlouge himself!

name: Princess Lion
flavor_text: The lion dance wards off evil and brings good fortune, but my dance is a little different. First, I salute my enemy. Then, I quickly destroy them with all my might before they can feel the pain or shame of defeat. This is my lion dance.
gacha_text: Want the lion to bite your head for luck?

name: Princess Lion
flavor_text: I am a lion, a ruler who can master any wild tiger. I see some are displeased that a lion would subdue a tiger. Very well. Come forth if you've the nerve. We shall settle this in our first fight of the year.
gacha_text: We shall settle this in our first fight of the year.

name: Princess White Rose
flavor_text: Lord Orlouge truly loved me like he loved his white roses. He gave me their name, and made me his 46th concubine. I would never betray him.

name: Princess White Rose
flavor_text: Don't tell me you couldn't eat them all because they're too sweet. I want you to finish them, finish all of them.
gacha_text:
You look wonderful in it,
though! So charming
and magical!
gacha_serif1: You look wonderful in it, though! So charming and magical!

name: Princess White Rose
flavor_text: I am White Rose. I surely once had another name, but I forgot it. I can be nothing but White Rose. This name represents all that I am. That is what becoming a concubine entails.

name: Princess White Rose
flavor_text: I wish to be true to my name as the noble white rose. Still, I love red and orange roses, too. Had I been Lord Orlouge's 16th concubine, I'd have been Princess Rainbow Rose.

name: Princess White Rose
flavor_text: Lord Orlouge asked me to educate Lady Asellus. We will fail unless we work together. I want to stay true to my feelings.
gacha_text: I will teach you everything about Mystics, about myself, and about Lord Orlouge.
gacha_serif1: Who... who are you?
gacha_serif2: Lady Asellus, I hope all is well.

name: Princess White Rose
flavor_text: The day when we jumped into the crimson flames together... When we walked through the snow barefoot in Mosperiburg... When I felt the warmth of your hand... It still comes back to me.
gacha_text: When I felt the warmth of your hand... It still comes back to me.

name: Princess White Rose
flavor_text: I was made to be her tutor, she who sleeps ever on. But I feel something will soon happen. Perhaps the day she wakes up is close. I have a feeling that it will be a special day for me.
gacha_text: These coffins are our refuge as well as our prison.
gacha_serif1: Lord Orlouge took my blood, making me a mystic. By ending my human life, he granted me eternal life.

name: Princess White Rose
flavor_text: And now I await Lady Asellus in my new costume. It always gets me nervous. How will she look at me? What will she say? She never reacts how a Mystic would. I can't wait.
gacha_text: You seem to be in a good mood, Lady Asellus.
gacha_serif1: Oh, Sir Knight. You truly did come for me!

name: Virgil
flavor_text: Will you be able to satisfy me? Will there be fireworks? That is the question. Fight me with all your heart and entertain me.
gacha_text: This should be lots of fun!
gacha_serif1: I've been waiting for you.

name: Virgil
flavor_text: I'll play precisely on the beat but with passion. The rest of you need only follow my lead. Now, let's show the audience the best combo they've ever seen!
gacha_text: Are you having fun?

name: Nusakan
flavor_text: Mystic or not, I will see you if you are sick. Many a terrible disease is caused by demons of illness. Some possess monsters, some humans. I now seek one possessing a Mec.
gacha_text: Next, please.
gacha_serif1: What is a doctor even doing here, anyway?
gacha_serif2: A doctor, like any good scholar, is curious about their work and wants to learn more.

name: Time Lord
another_name: [Why Did You Turn My Clock On?]
flavor_text: I studied Time Magic and mastered it. Then I stopped my time to endlessly savor that moment. But now, something is rapidly fading from within me. Something I'll never regain. So, let me ask you...
gacha_text: Why did you turn my clock on?

name: Time Lord
flavor_text: Now, the audience's time almost stands still. During this time, endless sounds flow in and etch into their subconscious. Infinite emotions with every note I play. Only I can play time like this.
gacha_text: Seems there is interesting time magic yet to find.

name: Mesarthim
flavor_text: I want to leave the lake and travel the world, but I worry whether a Water Mystic can live away from it. After all, I don't have the strength of those nobles.
gacha_text: The scent of a noble Mystic... But how? She's human.
gacha_serif1: Ask of me what you will. I am your servant.
gacha_serif2: No, you are not my servant.

name: Mesarthim
flavor_text: I know there are good humans as there are also a great deal of evil Mystics. But the stench of humans is repulsive. My mind tries to resist, but my nose rejects it.
gacha_text: I can't stand the stench of humans. I find myself choking on it...
gacha_serif1: I can smell the lake!

name: Mesarthim
flavor_text: With a noble heart, she was kind enough to talk to someone as lowly as I am. Thanks to her, I had the courage to overcome great difficulties. I offer prayers of deep gratitude to the savior of my soul.
gacha_text: Thanks to her, I had the courage to overcome great difficulties.

name: Mesarthim
flavor_text: People think I'm a gloomy mystic. And they're right. As such, is it possible for me to be a bringer of good luck? It makes me terribly anxious. But, you know, I want to do my best.
gacha_text: You know, I want to do my best.

name: King Sei
flavor_text: My ancestor unified the lands of Shrike with martial arts and was dubbed King Mu of war. I inherited those lands and made of them a nation. Thus am I King Sei of completion.

name: King Sei
flavor_text: I rush over to answer the call, and what do I find but a ghostly test of courage! Let the monsters handle it, I say. I am the King of Shrike. Frightening children is not my job!
gacha_text: Only those I deem worthy may pass.
gacha_serif1: Skeleton? I am the King of Shrike.

name: Thunder
flavor_text: Bad guys, huh?! Leave it to me, Big Bro! Yeah, I'm not good for much, except when it comes to going on a rampage! You just stand back and give me some music to get me goin'.

name: Kylin
flavor_text: Only one being in the whole universe can possess the gift of Space Magic, and I cannot protect this Paradise without it. The children need this Paradise. I will not give up the gift to you!
gacha_text: It will be yours, if you beat me!

name: Red Turnip
flavor_text: Just Red Turnip is fine. Call me Miss Red Turnip, or whatever, and I'm bound to blush as red as a-- wait, my whole body is normally red! Bwa ha ha!

name: Red Turnip
flavor_text: There's an extra special gift just for the good kids. It's more fun than any toy! It's the cutest and coolest out there! It's me! Heh heh heh!
gacha_text: It's the cutest and coolest out there!

name: BJ&K
flavor_text: I have your test results. No problem here... which is odd considering your usual behavior. I'd say it's abnormal. It is possible that the sample was swapped. Time to test again!
gacha_text: I follow orders.
gacha_serif1: We have a big problem!
gacha_serif2: No problem here.

name: ZEKE
flavor_text: Fireworks are being set off on the riverbanks near the onsens. They are not anti-aircraft fire. Even if they were, I could avoid getting hit, of course! Flying at night is the best!
gacha_text: Flying at night is the best!

name: ZEKE
flavor_text: Air resistance is nice and low at ultra-high altitudes. It makes a massive difference to my flight performance. Man, I don't want to go back to the surface!
gacha_text: Can you take me with you?
gacha_serif1: How can you activate me in this tiny space?

name: pzkwV
flavor_text: What makes a lucky find? It depends on who's looking. That's why you can find something you like in junk shops like this. Of course, it's also because this shop gets the good stuff.
gacha_text: Please take me with you.
gacha_serif1: Hi! How are you?
gacha_serif2: Doctor?! You became a mec?

name: Engineer Car
flavor_text: Machines that fight on the front line are important, but they must be serviced and maintained. The Engineer Car is an all-purpose mech that can perform repairs under the harshest battlefield conditions.

name: Engineer Car
flavor_text: Party composition should be flexible to suit the mission, especially when it's a mech corps. Just make sure you add Engineer Car to the corps, whatever the mission.
gacha_text: I am an Engineer Car, programmed to analyze and fix all kinds of mechs.

name: Engineer Car
flavor_text: Even I can upgrade my battle capabilities if I can load myself with more weapons. It's mean to try and box me into engineering because I'm an Engineer Car. I can become a Battle Car. See?
gacha_text: I can become a Battle Car. See?
gacha_serif1: Recharged!

name: Alkarl
flavor_text: Where there is evil, there is a hero. No evil is overlooked in any region by Santuario. If evil finds you, call for a hero in your heart. If your heart is true, your voice will surely reach Santuario.
gacha_text: Heroes must only use their power for truth and justice.
gacha_serif1: It was the only way to save your life. I had to make you a hero.

name: Alkarl
flavor_text: Heroes must use their power for good. They must not reveal their true identities. I'll be watching you to make sure you follow the hero's code of honor. Monitoring you? No, I only want to see you in action.
gacha_text: Use your power for anything but a just cause... and you're dead.
gacha_serif1: But you must also follow the hero's code of honor.

name: Rastaban
flavor_text: There's no such thing as a new year for mystics. Time simply flows, unchanging. But I want to mark the years as humans do. I would like to wait for a new year to herald a new world.
gacha_text: I would like to wait for a new year to herald a new world.

name: Rastaban
flavor_text: The Charm Lord gave the human girl a drop of his blood. A mere drop of blood, but I feel that it will change the world. What was thought to be nothing will upturn Chateau Aiguille from its foundation. The time has come.

name: Leonard (SF1)
flavor_text: They call me a genius. I'm like this due to my rich education in Trinity. Anyone could do the same. Rather, nothing will come of doing nothing.

name: Leonard (SF1)
flavor_text: I have a Mec body now, but it's no problem at all. My processing speed is unchanged, but I can now multitask perfectly. I can continue my own research while tending to your requests.
gacha_text: I am still Leonard.
gacha_serif1: How should I call you?
gacha_serif2: I've left a copy of my mind in this machine, just for times like this. I guess now we're brothers.

name: Rocky
flavor_text: Success! I always wanted to try transforming into one of these guys. How I envied the way girls hugged and petted them. This kind of punishment game is my favorite!

name: Cindy Campbell
flavor_text: You want to talk business? I love a good business proposition. Now, I'm a fun-loving gal, so I'd rather avoid heated fights. But if you get in the way of my business, I'll string you up nice and high.
gacha_text: That's really odd.
gacha_serif1: Well, the problem is, it's a fictitious company. You know, it doesn't exist. No one knows how to contact them.
gacha_serif2: Why don't you contact them?

name: Berva
flavor_text: The pleasure of going all out, your adrenaline pumping to the max. You know how it feels when your blood boils and bubbles. Fighting weaklings just doesn't do it! But today I feast!
gacha_text: Now it's your funeral.
gacha_serif1: You made it here, eh? We could use someone like you in our army. Heh, heh.

name: Shuzer
flavor_text: I, for one, love to see people suffer. And mental anguish? That hits the spot. When you're in pain, you gotta scream it out and writhe. It's no fun if you hold it in. Come on, scream!
gacha_text: Prepare to meet your mother and sister.
gacha_serif1: You must be Okonogi's brat.

name: Orlouge
flavor_text: Everyone desires to yield to an almighty being. Their lives are easier without the heavy burden that is choice. Give your hearts to me. Don't be bound by liberty. A life of joy is its own reward.

name: Orlouge
flavor_text: Mystic hierarchy is absolute. It is impossible for the low to defy the high. Mystics are above other races. Our actions are not beholden to such notions as the law of the land.
gacha_text: I shall build a nation of Mystics in this world. Yes, a fine idea, I must say.
gacha_serif1: The blue blood of a Mystic and the red blood of a human are both inside your body.

name: Orlouge
flavor_text: The value of a Mystic lies in their strength. I had some hopes for you, but they were misplaced. Not even my own blood could produce someone to rival me. Time for you to vanish, weakling.
gacha_text: Let me put you out of your misery.
gacha_serif1: Perhaps I made a terrible mistake saving a worthless human life.

name: Thyme
flavor_text: I'm Captain Thyme! I'm the Captain, of course--we're called the Thyme Expedition Team. Be quiet, sis. You too, Uncle Taco. Gen, stop drinking. And T260G, let's go!
gacha_text: Heh, heh, Sir Thyme. That's weird.
gacha_serif1: I'm Thyme. I dug you out of the crater. You ought to be grateful.

name: Gustave
flavor_text: The power of steel is the power of human will. Let steel, not magic, be the source of your power. When you do, your path will open up before you.

name: Gustave
flavor_text: Raise the troops' morale? Damn you, Kelvin... You talk like it's so easy. Why would the words of a failure like me boost their spirits? I'll tell them this and it'll be all they should need: Onward, into battle!
gacha_text:
Aaahh...
For some reason, I feel my heart lifting. It's been a
while since I've felt this way.
gacha_serif1: Motherrrr... !

name: Gustave
flavor_text: I conquered the entire Eastern Continent, and the city of Hahn Nova is being rebuilt. It may become the greatest city in the world. But what now? Who wants a reject for a ruler?

name: Gustave
flavor_text: Whoever wins this battle wins the throne. I've no interest in the throne, but for the sake of my friends who've stuck by me, I will win. And above all, I must win for Mother.
gacha_text:
I just want to see
what I am capable of.

name: Gustave
flavor_text: To think so many people are unskilled in magic. The downtrodden. Those with nothing to lose. They are led by me, a man with no Anima. I should be the first to fall, since no one would mourn my death.
gacha_text: No one's asking you to do it. I'll take care of it myself.
gacha_serif1: Tell every commander that we aren't taking any prisoners.

name: Gustave
flavor_text: Master, I've gone too far. I'm not strong enough to swing this sword in a real battle. It might be good for training. But the sword I intend to forge is much, much bigger.
gacha_text: Teach me how to do it. I want to make a steel sword.
gacha_serif1: Gustave, 14 years old

name: Gustave
flavor_text: I've got a good feeling about this new sword. I'm going to a cave to try it out on some monsters right away. Both my sword-making skills and my swordsmanship have improved. I can fight by myself now.
gacha_text: Would it be the sword that is tested, or me myself?
gacha_serif1: This is how you use a sword.

name: Gustave
flavor_text: Many Animas were sacrificed in the name of Gustave. It is time I answered for that. It matters not who did it. This outcome was my fate and I wish to involve no one else in it.
gacha_text: Hurry up and go!
gacha_serif1: I don't want to say good-bye!
gacha_serif2: On top of that, they only want ME! The more distance you put between us, the better your chances are.

name: Wil
flavor_text: I'm Wil. I came here looking for my first job as a digger. What do you say? Shall we form a party? The more in our ranks, the greater the peace of mind.
gacha_text: It must be somewhere on this ship. I'm gonna sink the Egg to the bottom of the sea!
gacha_serif1: Of course.
gacha_serif2: Understood.

name: Wil
flavor_text: I'm a digger, so to return the favor, I give Quells instead of chocolates. This is a special kind of Quell that'll warm your heart.

name: Wil
flavor_text: This isn't alcohol. Nothing beats this after a soak. It replenishes the Anima within. Anima permeate every part of us. And this? Let's just say it tastes even better at my age. Ho ho ho!

name: Wil
flavor_text: The day for presents has come! I want all the children to be happy tomorrow morning. I've got a lot of presents to deliver. Ones that a rich person would covet.
gacha_text: Merry Christmas! Ho ho ho!
gacha_serif1: Merry Christmas! Ho ho ho!

name: Wil
flavor_text: Ninjas! To think one could hone Anima like this! There were assassins who could control it in Sandail, too. So, this is what it feels like. I could get used to this.
gacha_text: Ninjas! To think one could hone Anima like this!

name: Wil
flavor_text: I'm just starting out, but I want to be a great digger like my father one day. Aunty Nina said a good digger is an experienced digger, so I just gotta get out there and find Quells.
gacha_text: How about it, would you like to join my expedition?
gacha_serif1: Oh, what is it? Did you miss the expedition too?
gacha_serif2: I am Wil. I've come here to look for my first job as a digger.

name: Rich
flavor_text: I'm Rich... in name only, I'm afraid, seeing as I'm flat broke. No matter how many Quells I dig up, I never seem to have any money. Why is that?

name: Rich
flavor_text: I'll protect my family. I won't let something like the Egg threaten them.

name: Rich
flavor_text: Why're you looking at me like that? It's not like I sold any presents. I just got an advance on my Santa salary, so I'm filling up the tank before takeoff. Share a toast on this holy night?
gacha_text: I'm Rich Knights. How about we make a rainbow appear over this Holy Night winter wonderland?
gacha_serif1: I'm always getting the cold shoulder, but tonight is different... What do I do?

name: Rich
flavor_text: Having no money simply means I know how to enjoy life without it. Take this hot tofu for example. It doesn't cost as much as the finest meat, but it really warms yah hasafashafsas--
gacha_text: I want to eat good food.

name: Rich
flavor_text: I'm not going to let you set foot in North Gate again, let alone my father's place. I don't know why you lured me here, but it's over. I'll do what I failed to do in Westia.
gacha_text: Didn't you want to fight? Forget all this gibberish and come get some.
gacha_serif1: Wasn't I just scum to you?
gacha_serif2: I've been waiting for you, Rich.

name: Ginny
flavor_text: Anima reside in all things in the world. Both living creatures, as well as inanimate objects. The forest is filled with Anima. Anima of the forest, lend me your power!

name: Ginny
flavor_text: I myself am the youngest in a proud line of Knights diggers. I know all too well how dangerous it is to get one's hands on Quells. Are you ready? Let's go.
gacha_text:
Dad... Mom... Grandpa...
Everyone... Don't let the Egg
beat you!

name: Ginny
flavor_text: Ha-haaa, I'm not cold at all, even if I'm dressed like this. I have Quells in my pocket that keep me warm. All right! Time to give out some presents!
gacha_text:
What a great idea! Everyone'll
be so happy.

name: Ginny
flavor_text: This relaxes me head to toes. It makes me feel whole. This Peg toy is cute, don't you think? Sorry for hitting you earlier. Seems the old folks are having a soak now, so I'll wait.
gacha_text: Come here and we'll go in together.
gacha_serif1: Over here, Claudia! Come on in!

name: Ginny
flavor_text: The Egg is a long-time enemy of my grandfather. It attracts vile Anima. I will not lose to such Anima. I am scared, though. Father, give me strength!
gacha_text: Fighting for someone is such a great feeling.
gacha_serif1: I feel so at peace for some reason. Such a mysterious feeling...

name: Ginny
flavor_text: Soft candy for Grandpa... And I'll get these eel goby for Primiera! She might get super mad, though. And then she would stuff them into Roberto's mouth and say, "Thanks, Ginny. It's tasty."
gacha_text: Aw, I want a souvenir, too!

name: Kelvin
flavor_text: As a noble, I have a duty to lead the common folk and to uphold high standards of propriety. There is no time to fool around. That's what Gustave doesn't see. And he's a royal! What do I do with him?
gacha_text: Don't worry about it. It's for Madam Sophie.
gacha_serif1: ...You don't need to think about anything. Go see Madam Sophie. If you feel like crying, then cry. If you want to leave her with a smile, then smile.

name: Leslie
flavor_text: Leaving for new places holds the promise of new meetings--from Gruegel to Jade to Thermes. But this trip is completely different. It'll be a new land for me. Oh, the people I'll meet!
gacha_text: New lands are always so exciting.
gacha_serif1: Back then, I was really scared, I wanted to run away, but I hated the idea of running, so I gathered the courage to stay.
gacha_serif2: Leslie, why do you cry?

name: Leslie
flavor_text: I was right to drag you here. I haven't seen you like this in a long time. Flynn and Kelvin know what this break means and they're enjoying it--they're such good friends. We all love you, you know.
gacha_text: It's nice to have friends to fool around with.
gacha_serif1: The type of clientele looks different from last time, though. They're a little... rough for tourists.

name: Flynn
flavor_text: Across the sea... The land where you were born is there, Sir Gus. I know it's impossible, but how I would love to see it. I bet going there would make me a whole new person.

name: Flynn
flavor_text: There are akebia here, too. We share a lot of memories with those, don't we, Sir Gus? You probably don't need akebia now that you can eat whatever you want, but how about a bite?

name: Flynn
flavor_text: However scary a monster is, just avoid it. Stop, move forward, change direction, then slip right by it before you're even within range of its attacks. No matter how weak you are, or even if you can't use magic, you can't lose if you just don't fight.
gacha_text: Would it be all right if I wait here?
gacha_serif1: Sir Gus, I'm scared. There are monsters here, right?

name: Cielmer
flavor_text: I thought I knew everything there was to know about Anima. But Gustave proved me wrong. By getting to know him, I was able to further explore the world of Anima. In a sense, he was my teacher.
gacha_text: If it doesn't bother you, allow me to travel with you.
gacha_serif1: Sophie's Anima will always be with you.
gacha_serif2: I will try to believe so, Master Cielmer.

name: Nebelstern
flavor_text: No matter how capable a general is, victory will only be achieved if his soldiers follow him. He must lead the way and set an example for his men. The enemy may kill him, but courage is of utmost importance to a general.

name: Nebelstern
flavor_text: A cup of tea in the early morning. The aroma wakes my senses. The mellow sweetness and slight bitterness in my mouth spread through my body, and my faculties are quickened. I'm ready for the day.
gacha_text: I'm ready for the day.

name: Johan
flavor_text: Adapt your Anima to your surroundings. Doing so will remove all indications of your presence. You can move all you like, even stand right in front of your adversaries, and they will have no idea that you're there.

name: Johan
flavor_text: Soon the scorpion will crawl up to the back of my neck. Its venom will spread through my veins, and I will die. I am fine with this. After all, it was I who chose to live a life of freedom.

name: Johan
flavor_text: I'll show you what my Assassin Arts are all about! Until the day the Scorpions come for me!

name: Johan
flavor_text: My fate changed the day I met Master Gustave. I lived to see this day, and it'll be my last. The days I was given a reason to live were amazing. Goodbye, Ven, my true friend.
gacha_text: I'll show you what my Assassination Arts are all about!
gacha_serif1: Are you sure about this, Johan?
gacha_serif2: Just order me to defend this position.

name: Johan
flavor_text: Not yet, Scorpion. I've got one more big guy to finish. I can't protect Master Gustave if I don't kill 'em. Just give me enough time to get close to the enemy!
gacha_text: I'm sure I can fight far better than you, even in this state.
gacha_serif1: I'll look out for Master Gustave.

name: Ventarbre
flavor_text: Everything has an Anima. Feel it. Those are Master Cielmer's teachings. It is said that books contain the author's Anima. I would also like to leave behind my Anima someday.
gacha_text: I am Ventarbre. Just call me Ven.
gacha_serif1: Are you okay? Your injuries look bad.

name: Cordelia
flavor_text: I may be a novice, but I am a sentry too. I have what it takes. I only lack experience. Oh, my name is Cordelia. Nice to meet you.
gacha_text:
I might not look like much,
but I have confidence in
my abilities. I only lack
experience.
gacha_serif1: I'm Cordelia. We sentries guard diggers like you. Nice to meet you, Wil.

name: Cordelia
flavor_text: Have some Quells! ...I wish I could say that, but for today, you'll have to settle for some homemade chocolates. I really like you, so... I want you to have these.

name: Cordelia
flavor_text: I'm using a special spell to make kitty here more comfy. It really works, huh? Doesn't help for travels on the road, but it's my signature move. Does it work on people too? I don't know. I've never tried it.

name: Cordelia
flavor_text: Each of these presents will bring a smile to a child's face somewhere. I am enveloped in happiness right now with joy in the palm of my hands. This deed warms my heart.
gacha_text: At this rate, we won't be able to deliver all the presents before the night is up.
gacha_serif1: How're things over there, Labelle?

name: Cordelia
flavor_text: I don't know enough about this world. I must learn more to fight more effectively. And this is the perfect spot to do so. I'd also like to learn more about... you.
gacha_text: I must learn more to fight more effectively.

name: Cordelia
flavor_text: I wonder why I feel like going for a walk on a moonlit night. Maybe Anima is connected to the moon. Wil used to say that it was hard to find Quells during full moons. I wonder how he's doing.
gacha_text: Isn't the moon lovely?

name: Cordelia
flavor_text: We sentries detect dangerous Anima so diggers can focus on Quell Anima. We will not take unnecessary risks until we reach our destination. That's an ironclad rule of adventuring.
gacha_text: I'm going to have to go with you as your sentry.
gacha_serif1: All the way to Gruegel... I've heard stories, but I've never been there myself.

name: Narcisse
flavor_text: Where there's a Quell, there are monsters. Any digger worth their salt is bound to find trouble. As such, a skilled sentry guarantees a digger's results. Teaming up with me is the way to go.
gacha_text: Teaming up with me is the way to go.
gacha_serif1: My name is Wil. I'm a novice digger.
gacha_serif2: I am Narcisse, a spell caster. I came here to join a Quell expedition.

name: Narcisse
flavor_text: Most people can use spells to some degree, but if you call yourself a spell caster, you can't be like most people. A spell caster must understand the nature of the Anima and ways to draw out its power.
gacha_text: You don't hesitate, do you, Wil?
gacha_serif1: I have to go see for myself, what my father saw.
gacha_serif2: The Desert Megalith... If you really want me to, I guess I can lend you a hand.

name: Tyler
flavor_text: The most important thing sentries do is detect and avoid danger. But sometimes you need to face it. Do you have the courage? It's dangerous here. I'll go first.
gacha_text: How about it? You want to work together?
gacha_serif1: I'm Tyler. I've come here to look for treasure.

name: Labelle
flavor_text: The woods are full of Anima. Those who don't care for the woods, don't care for Anima. You value Anima, don't you? I wonder if you would treat my Anima with the same care...
gacha_text: Let's go then.
gacha_serif1: You do?!
gacha_serif2: I know another way there.

name: Labelle
flavor_text: This night gives my heart warmth. When you think of another's Anima, your own Anima warms up. Strange, isn't it? That's why I welcome the downhearted to my party. Please, step right in.
gacha_text: Rrrgh! Now where did Wil and Rich get off to?!
gacha_serif1: We'll just have to do what we can. It's now a race to finish before sunrise.

name: Diana (SF2)
flavor_text: No luck again? That's okay. Your coming home safe and sound is the best gift I could ask for. Now, come here and give me a big hug until all of my worries melt away.
gacha_text: Richard! Come home soon.
gacha_serif1: I'm having one.
gacha_serif2: Huh? What're you having?

name: Julia
flavor_text: This isn't a dream, is it? My rainbow fades every morning, but this one's real. Now, we can cultivate the land. People will return to this place. This is just the beginning of my dream.
gacha_text: I'm seeing my rainbow come true...
gacha_serif1: It's like a dream...

name: Eleanor
flavor_text: I take a bigger cut, naturally, but that's better than making a mistake, no? Research and intel gathering are vital to finding Quells, and I'm quite thorough about it. You rely too much on your talents, you know.
gacha_text: It'll be a breeze, now that I'm here.
gacha_serif1: Actually, I'm in the middle of exploring the cave. It's not as easy as I thought it would be. Will you join me?
gacha_serif2: I thought so. Yeah, we'll help.

name: Roberto
flavor_text: Ginny fights valiantly for her family. And I am the cool hero who protects her. I'm like the protagonist of an adventure novel. How can you not call this fate?
gacha_text: Ugh! Guess I have to fight!
gacha_serif1: We will be victorious. This thing...

name: Roberto
flavor_text: I know a good saying for when you lose your way: let the Anima guide you. Just take the first step, and the rest will follow. Where should we stay tonight? Let the Anima guide you!
gacha_text: I'm Roberto. I make my living around here.
gacha_serif1: Now, now, don't be too harsh. Running away after her grandpa is very brave of her.

name: Primiera
flavor_text: A nobleman's daughter is just a tool in his fight for power. I left because I didn't want that fate for myself. Even as I face evil Anima, my heart is filled with joy. This is where I'll spend my days.
gacha_text: Stepmother, father, give me power!
gacha_serif1: Such an overwhelming Anima! It feels like it's piercing my body...

name: Primiera
flavor_text: I feel a bit uneasy without my armor. But what's this sense of freedom? It feels like I've shed armor from not just my body, but my heart as well. I feel so light, like I have wings.

name: Primiera
flavor_text: Feel the weapon's Anima as I move. Hold the weapon every day until I can move it as I feel it. Only daily training will strongly connect my weapon with my Anima.
gacha_text: Don't underestimate me because I'm a woman.
gacha_serif1: I've done nothing that needs forgiving in the first place.

name: Meythia
flavor_text: If you can feel Stone Anima, you can handle any stone axe at will, no matter how big it is. Master Ven taught me that. I feel so comfortable with the Anima of the stone axe, even more than with people!
gacha_text: What a horrible thing to do.
gacha_serif1: Master Ven, you sent me to take this on, knowing how powerful it is?

name: Gustaf
flavor_text: Firebrand, the royal symbol of Finney, and the great steel sword forged by Marquis Gustave himself. With these two legendary swords, the Egg's ambitions will be cut down! Hopefully I can achieve that...
gacha_text: Oh Firebrand, can I put my faith in you?
gacha_serif1: The Firebrand... It's resonating with the Egg!

name: Gustaf
flavor_text: The steel sword negates Anima. You don't want to use your power more than necessary before reaching your destination. I'll lead the way, and we can avoid needless confrontation. (That is, if the Firebrand doesn't attract unwanted Anima.)
gacha_text: No, it's not that. Alright, I'll go.
gacha_serif1: If it really is a Megalith, isn't it a bit too dangerous?

name: Misty
flavor_text: I had a realization as I grew with this body. People have all kinds of Anima. Some are no good. But the Knights Anima is good. No, it's magnificent! You will be my next vessel.
gacha_text: I want your Anima.
gacha_serif1: What kind of ridiculous statement is that? What are you really up to?
gacha_serif2: Something occurred to me when I saw how powerful you were. I want you.

name: Misty
flavor_text: I called and called and finally, I'm fished up off the ocean floor. Wil Knights, when I grow up, I'm going to kill you. Wait for me, okay? No dying before then. Your life is mine.

name: Peg
flavor_text: D-d-d-d-d-d-ash, dash, full-speed dash! D-d-d-d-d-d-ash, dash, full-speed dash!

name: Laura
flavor_text: Don't overextend yourself. Leave this area to me. After all, I could go on a rampage and no one's gonna say anything.

name: Laura
flavor_text: You haven't heard of the Sea Wolf? Must be your first time on the waves. Well, you have two choices. Either I take whatever treasure's on you, and you go back home and remember my name, or... I take your life and feed you to the fishes.

name: Laura
flavor_text: One after another, you just don't quit. Why don't you give up already? As long as I'm around, you won't get any closer. If you still want to go at it, then fine, I'll humor you.
gacha_text: Come any closer and you WILL get hurt!
gacha_serif1: What about it?!
gacha_serif2: You're Prince Henri of Escata, right?

name: Laura
flavor_text: It's amazing how beautiful mountains and trees can be. This beautiful landscape isn't just left to nature's devices, but it's created by people and nature together. It's good to leave things as they are, but it's also fine to add a nice touch.
gacha_text: It's good to leave things as they are, but it's also fine to add a nice touch.

name: Laura
flavor_text: Being at the fore is the most dangerous, which is why I go first. But I can see the enemy trembling, too. I can tell they're not ready, so I tear right in. It's exhilarating!
gacha_text: Being at the fore is the most dangerous, which is why I go first.
gacha_serif1: Oh, you know, I totally attract bad luck this way, like, all the time.
gacha_serif2: You're the one who decided to get on the same boat as us.

name: Ventus
flavor_text: Fast, reliable, and affordable. People don't know me yet, but I'm the Great Ventus, the best carrier. Just Ventus is fine, though. I'll deliver anything. Ventus, at your service!

name: Ventus
flavor_text: Blue sky, azure sea, and a long, curving beach hugged by green pines. Who knew such a nice place was out there? Oh, so it's called Niji No Matsubara, or Rainbow Pine Grove, for its arc shape!
gacha_text: Who knew such a nice place was out there?

name: Judie
flavor_text: Listen to this! So today, Mommy got mad at Roy again because he wouldn't eat his dinner. Then Marie got called next door. So... I'll make your dinner for you myself -- with magic!
gacha_text: It's OK. Just leave it to me!
gacha_serif1: Sure! You going out?
gacha_serif2: Judie, could you watch the shop?

name: Kurt
flavor_text: The world is chock-full of mysteries. Mysterious relics are scattered all over, their secrets waiting to be unraveled. Let's go on an adventure that'll lead us to the future of the world.
gacha_text: This world is also chock-full of mysteries.
gacha_serif1: I wouldn't do such a thing. I'm Kurt.
gacha_serif2: If you're asking for money, I'll pass on it.

name: Ruby
flavor_text: In any case, don't overthink it. Things always work out somehow. Tomorrow will come, no matter what your fortune reads. Otherwise, I'd be too scared to do fortunetelling.

name: Ruby
flavor_text: Let's go as high as it goes! I don't know if I'll ever get another chance to do this, so I wanna go as high up as possible. Past the clouds, up to the moon and even the stars! I'd love to take a couple of stars home.
gacha_text: Might as well have fun while we're at it.

name: Mythe
flavor_text: People wail and curse when they get dumped. How ugly they become when they think they own you, and then find out they don't. To me, love was a desire to own. Truly. Until I saw her.
gacha_text: This has never happened to me before.
gacha_serif1: Could I be in love?

name: Armic
flavor_text: I dunno which way to go. The wind's blowing from that direction, so maybe I should head that way. Why do I hafta go on this stupid journey? Won't someone tell me?
gacha_text: Aaah... I just want to go home.
gacha_serif1: Oh, is it an alphabet?

name: Henri
flavor_text: As King of Escata, I am ready to rebuild my nation. My people will surely look up to me as an example, so I carry that burden as well. I can do these things because of what Laura has taught me.

name: Henri
flavor_text: My father and mother are no longer in this world. All those dear people of Escata perished in the chaos of that night. I'll never see any of them again.

name: Iskandar
flavor_text: The name's Iskandar. I have a bit of a vested interest in the workings of the world. I'd very much like to see how you involve yourself with it. Just observing, though.

name: Iskandar
flavor_text: They say time flows at a steady pace. Do you buy that? In my youth, I felt I had time to spare. But now, days and years just pass me by. Centuries and millennia slip by in the blink of an eye.
gacha_text: Why, a year ago feels like just the other day.

name: Silver Emperor
flavor_text: This world must also battle darkness? My experience here should help in our own fight, but I don't hear the voices of Cat and Emerald. Things seem different. All I can do is keep moving forward.

name: Silver Emperor
flavor_text: Selma, I entrust this world's future to you. Should I lose my life... No, when I lose my life, I can bequeath my wishes upon you. It will be a great burden, but a worthwhile one. I love you.
gacha_text: Seeing her face, my resolve almost wavered.
gacha_serif1: ...Let me know when you're ready to depart.

name: Selma
flavor_text: Hmm... Yeah, sure. Someday, if I meet the right person. Someone kind and gentle, but noble-minded, like my father.

name: Selma
flavor_text: My father is fighting somewhere out there in the world. That thought gives me the strength to go on!
gacha_text:
No need for that tone.
What in the world
are you doing?
gacha_serif1: I don't care how dangerous it is! That just makes it all the better for sword training!

name: Selma
flavor_text: There's always someone by me, supporting me. I'm grateful, but sometimes I just wanna be alone. I wanna go somewhere all alone, strip naked and be free! No one can see the real me.
gacha_text:
This will let me
breathe underwater, right?
gacha_serif1: It isn't moving, so it's not a fish. There's... something beneath the waves.

name: Selma
flavor_text: You are the customer, Father. I'm the shop owner. Hello, can I take your order? Oh, we don't serve alcohol. Would tea be okay? Here you go. Have some cake, too! It's delicious.
gacha_text: I'm lonely, but I'll be okay.
gacha_serif1: My apologies. I have acted so childish in front of you all...

name: Selma
flavor_text: That's Butcher's Sea Devil right there! I will not tolerate pirates in these waters! Ready your aim and fire! No need for warning shots. Send it to the depths!
gacha_text: Ready your aim and fire!

name: Urpina
flavor_text: Today, Elysed is coming to visit. If I'm not better behaved than usual, I'll make a fool of myself in front of her. But I think I can squeeze in some monster exterminating before she arrives.

name: Urpina
flavor_text: Two swords is the fighting style of my family, the House of Julanius. Even if I cannot handle them as well as my father or brother, it is a skill I too must learn. Now come, Mondo. Fight me.
gacha_text:
Brother... I did it. Your little
sister did it.
gacha_serif1: Brother... I'll kill... No way! I can't do it!

name: Urpina
flavor_text: What led me here? A Deity, or a Demonic Overlord? If this is fate, all I can do is fight for the honor of House Julanius! I'll face it head on, fearless, with all my might!
gacha_text:
For the honor of
House Julanius!

name: Urpina
flavor_text: I've finally mastered the dual wielding technique of House Julanius. Brother's still leagues beyond me, but I'd like to present the technique to everyone who supported me!
gacha_text: Urpina Finish!
gacha_serif1: Mother wielded a fearsome blade at Father's side, and I shall do no less for the House of Julanius!

name: Urpina
flavor_text: I've finally mastered the zero-wielding technique even my brother could not master! I've still a long way to go, but I won today thanks to everyone who supported me!
gacha_text: I'm ready!
gacha_serif1: I should've brushed up on my martial arts, considering you both shall be using them.

name: Leonard (SSG)
flavor_text: Hey, are we doing this or not? How about this: whoever wins is right.

name: Leonard (SSG)
flavor_text: This is our traditional victory pose. After fighting with all our might, we squat down to take a break. Let me do what I want.
gacha_text: You all just keep coming, don't you?
gacha_serif1: All right, that oughta do it for the harvest. I finished the fastest again this year for sure.

name: Leonard (SSG)
flavor_text: I've never seen a lion. Even so, I know how this lion dance goes. All I gotta do is make the little kids cry, right? I've got this. That's a talent of mine.
gacha_text: I'll let the lion bite your head for luck.

name: Taria
flavor_text: I had fun with my witchcraft when I was young. I thought I could do anything, but that was not so. No magic can change your heart. Perhaps I was destined to use this power once more.
gacha_text: Don't expect too much from me. I'm but a humble potter.
gacha_serif1: Kahn, you came. I must set out again.

name: Taria
flavor_text: Long ago, a potter far from home discovered how to calm his soul by grinding stone to powder, then forming and firing it to make porcelain. He could get lost in his work and forget all his worries. I know this feeling, for I too have things I wish to forget.
gacha_text: Porcelain making is big in this town.

name: Taria
flavor_text: Did you think I was a tennyo, here to bring you good fortune? Hate to break it to you, but I'm a witch. Not that witches will always bring you misfortune, but I just can't make you happy. You see, I like my freedom.
gacha_text: Being a tennyo would surely be boring.

name: Balmaint
flavor_text: This axe is for lopping off heads in one fell swoop. It's different from a battle axe that deals damage and takes you down in combat. Both are axes, but they are made and used very differently.
gacha_text: I have a hard time believing that, and yet...
gacha_serif1: Now make your last words.

name: Balmaint
flavor_text: Only those allowed by Imperial Law could carry out sentences. I was one of those people, but that doesn't make me special. I'm just an average guy.

name: Balmaint
flavor_text: On the executioner's stand, the criminal is the protagonist. My role is to support that final moment. But today, the protagonist is an executioner, so I'll play it as best I can.
gacha_text: I'll play it as best I can.

name: Elisabeth
flavor_text: I know looking for Ei-Hanum is important, but we might as well explore while we're at it. You know, like go sight-seeing, grab a meal... It sure is great to escape my old man's watchful eye!

name: Elisabeth
flavor_text: I'm sure you realize you did something wrong. But you're sorely mistaken if you think it'll all be fine with an apology. You have to pay for what you did. So, which will it be? Left or right hand?
gacha_text: They must face the music. I won't turn a blind eye.
gacha_serif1: "Suit yourself"? What's that supposed to mean! You don't get to tell me that! Got it?! Let's get going already!

name: Kahn
flavor_text: I adventure with a group called the Killers. Was a guardsman for the Emperor and Grand Empress Dowager, but it became a pain. See, my thing is fighting while protecting. Name's Kahn. It's a pleasure.

name: Kahn
flavor_text: Relaxing with some food and drink. Best way to spend the New Year's, if you ask me. And with a stellar view and some entertainment, it's even better.
gacha_text: Why don't you put on a show?

name: Arthur Darlton
flavor_text: There are those who struggle and run from the law. I am not one of them. After all, if you use the law well, you can live a very comfortable life. You just come to me if you have any trouble.
gacha_text: You just come to me if you have any trouble.
gacha_serif1: Whoa, hold on! How is this about me now? Arthur Darlton is a bona fide, one-hundred-percent authentic legal clerk of Castle Kohan! Certainly not some Imperial Library spy.

name: Antonius
flavor_text: You will not always have the same sword. Weight, balance, and grip all affect your skills. So it is with hearts. No two people are the same. Act accordingly.
gacha_text: By the blade of House Julanius.
gacha_serif1: Leave it to me, Urpina.

name: Strumiknen
flavor_text: I'm a mercenary. I give my employer victory, protection, whatever I'm asked. But I ain't your slave. You can't tell me what to do if you haven't beat me in a fight.
gacha_text: You wanna beef with me, pal, you best come at me with all you got.
gacha_serif1: Huh, you're sharper than you look. Nice. Now I really do wanna fight with you. That axe ain't just for show, I hope!

name: Elysed
flavor_text: My sweet Elysed is the Lady of House Gwynese. Her noble heart, her manners, and her sense of fashion all make her my role model. The fact that she is engaged to my brother makes Urpina feel truly blessed.

name: Elysed
flavor_text: The chaos that followed the Empire's collapse, the power struggle between the three branch houses of House Gwynese... The Spirit Forest makes me forget all of that. But if I entrust my body to Spiritual energy too much, I'd lose control and perish.
gacha_text: Thank you, Urpina.
gacha_serif1: You've done it. Me, my father, and the Sublime Spiritual... You saved us all.

name: Ogniana
flavor_text: This is Grumon Queendom territory. There's a toll for passin' through the streets. And I won't allow anyone to weasel out of payin' it. I'm collectin' it one way or another.

name: Ogniana
flavor_text: Phew. What a day. Workin' hard sure gets you ready for a drink and some grub. But we had a ton of fun with them tax evaders. Here's to puttin' in the good work again tomorrow!
gacha_text: Cheers to the new world!

name: Sasha
flavor_text: Who I am matters not. This world's spiritual energy is in disarray. We must find out why and restore balance. I'd love to have your help. You won't say no, will you?
gacha_text: Who I am matters not.
gacha_serif1: Who I am matters not. As upset as the flow of spiritual energy is here, it'd be awful if one were to now use the Firebringer shards.

name: Tsubaki
flavor_text: Witches have stolen everything from me. I shall hunt them down and put an end to witches. That is my raison d'etre. Some say witches aren't real or that witch-hunting is illegal. No. They won't take this from me.
gacha_text: Put an end to witches!
gacha_serif1: I see. In that case, heard you the rumors of the witch who inhabits this region? Or have you perchance espied her yourself?

name: Macha
flavor_text: It seems that someone summoned me. Now that I'm here, I'll take over this world. I am Macha, the Celestial of sorcery. With magic, all is well in the world. Worship me, mortals! Follow the power of magic!
gacha_text: Let's have some fun!

name: Macha
flavor_text: This world is also filled with Spiritual energy. When used properly, there's no need to bring in beings from other worlds. Here, I'll teach you. After all, I am Macha, the Celestial of sorcery!

name: Macha
flavor_text: I saw the Spirituals gathering, so I came to have some fun and I see you're having some kind of festival. Is it for me? It's not? Well, a festival is always fun, whoever it's for.
gacha_text: A festival is always fun.

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: Prakity Prakian. That was the circus Liz and I were in. Who would've thought the ringmaster would...

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: Father... I know somehow the Shucho Arts will reveal the truth to me. I have inherited them from you. I'm still learning how to use them, but I am up to the task, Father.
gacha_text: Not just my father, but my mother, too. I feel they're watching over Liz and me now.

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: Out of desperation, I almost went down a bad path. But Liz was there to keep me on the straight and narrow. Somehow, just barely... I made it through alive.
gacha_text: Happy New Year everyone. Please lend me your strength this year, too.
gacha_serif1: Actually, this is my first time celebrating the New Year like this, so I'm not sure what to do.

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: There's a shark warning?! I can't let Liz go into the water! Here, this flamingo will be your bait. Hang on tight! And don't get the wrong idea, of course I can swim without it!

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: When Jo was born, I was so happy. I thought I would be her father. That's why I was against hiding her in Mazewood. I am the only one who can protect Jo. I cannot leave her protection to someone else.

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: I inherited the Shucho Arts from my father. But I need to learn even stronger Shucho magic. I must become stronger. If I don't, I won't be able to protect my family and Jo.
gacha_text: If I don't, I won't be able to protect my family and Jo.
gacha_serif1: Jo was still a baby. She doesn't remember us at all.

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: Jo, you have the right to a happy life. Liz, live with Jo and always be at her side. Even if this defies fate, even if this body is consumed by the power of Shucho, I will protect Jo.
gacha_text: Our only choice is to go and fight with Jo. Let's go, Liz!
gacha_serif1: The demonic beasts have spotted us! Our only choice is to go and fight with Jo. Let's go, Liz!

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: As a Grave Knight, I have one final request for the Otherworld Warriors: Lend me your strength. I need your help to protect Jo and Bert. I know it's selfish of me, but I have to protect them no matter what.
gacha_text: Even if this body is consumed by the power of Shucho, I'll protect them!
gacha_serif1: So I decided I'm going to be responsible for the family for them. I'll protect us.

name: Rag Robin
flavor_text: I'm here to punish evil and keep the city safe! Why am I, the cool Masked Crusader Robin, being chased by bad guys? Can somebody please tell me?!
gacha_text: I'm sorry... Can I get another name?
gacha_serif1: I-I'm family, too.

name: Liz Lynn Wood
flavor_text: My brother became a Grave Knight to save me. There must be something I can do, too!

name: Liz Lynn Wood
flavor_text: I was trapped in that cave forever. This vacation is almost surreal. And I looove ice cream. Where did Polka go, by the way?
gacha_text:
Polka's life depends
on this... floatie.
Hee hee.
gacha_serif1: I think it suits you. Try it on.

name: Robingirl
flavor_text: What a perfect costume. Now no one, especially my brother, will know who I am. I've been dying to try this -- I'm now the Masked Crusader Robin! Hope some evildoers show up soon.

name: Liz Lynn Wood
flavor_text: The Genbu Arts control water. I have a natural gift for magic thanks to my parentage. Their power protects me. But from now on, it's my turn to use my power to protect others.
gacha_text: The only way to make it through this is to fight. I'm not running away.
gacha_serif1: I saw him, just for a brief moment. He's headed for the Arch Witch. I have to hurry!

name: Liz Lynn Wood
flavor_text: When I held Jo to my chest after she was born, I couldn't stop crying. I was so thankful. I swore to become stronger for you. I had to give you up to the care of others to continue my search for more strength.

name: Liz Lynn Wood
flavor_text: Water has no form and thus can take any form. That is the essence of Genbu Arts. But now, my mind and heart are dedicated to protecting Jo. I should put my all into the Genbu Arts and set my soul free. However, it's... so difficult. Jo, you are all I can think about.
gacha_text: I want to hug Jo with all my might.
gacha_serif1: Have you already forgotten how much trouble your recklessness has caused?

name: Liz Lynn Wood
flavor_text: Jo was enveloped by water when she was in me. I'll just embrace her with my heart of water. There's no need to force myself to be detached. Thank you, Jo, for helping me get a little closer to mastering the Genbu arts.
gacha_text: Have Jo and Genryu already...?!
gacha_serif1: Have Jo and Genryu already...?!

name: Liz Lynn Wood
flavor_text: Jo, Bert, I won't leave you in the hands of fate. I will protect you with all that I am so that you can live the way you want to. Don't ever despair, both of you. The future is yours to choose.
gacha_text: I will protect you with all that I am so that you can live the way you want to.
gacha_serif1: That's right, Bert. We're family.

name: Robingirl
flavor_text: Evil shan't flourish in the same world as Robin the Masked Crusader! I've always wanted to say that line. I love being an ally of justice!
gacha_text: No evil will go unpunished!
gacha_serif1: From the heavens above to the earth below... Do any evil, and Robingirl shall know! Demonic beasts beware!

name: Shen Du
flavor_text: Since long ago, we astronomers of Dae have interacted with the Johannes sect in the town of Lance. They may know something about Master Dahao's whereabouts.

name: Shen Du
flavor_text: I was always following in the footsteps of Master Dahao. However, the difference in talent was obvious and she only seemed to be getting further away. Even so, Master Dahao placed her last hope in me. I have to do this. I must.
gacha_text: In order to save me, Master Dahao chose to sacrifice herself...
gacha_serif1: It is as it sounds. In order to save me, Master Dahao chose to sacrifice herself...

name: Shen Du
flavor_text: O star gods, give me strength! This voice is the voice of Hyobi of the Lunar Node, purging the sins and impurities of the wicked. This breath is the breath of Taishogun of Venus, breaking the cursed chains of the wicked... Ack! I'll be killed before I finish the chant!
gacha_text: I must do this. I must.
gacha_serif1: O astrodice, bestow upon me your revelation!

name: Valdor
flavor_text: The lost memories belonging to the heroes from 300 years ago... The truth behind them may be hidden in the shrines scattered around the world.

name: Valdor
flavor_text: We live under one roof, through joy and sorrow. The lobster clan values married life as well.

name: Valdor
flavor_text: Look at the spiral! You are getting sleepy, sleeeepy... What? No! I'm not trying to hypnotize you. This spiral has the power to unearth the truth. The truth!
gacha_text: Look at the spiral!
gacha_serif1: Having trouble sleeping, Polka?

name: Valdor
flavor_text: Listen up. Results are the product of ability and time. That is to say, if two people have the same ability, the one who puts in more time will achieve superior results. So, how do you surpass someone better than you? Only training will do, of course!
gacha_text: Time is a limited resource. Do not waste it.
gacha_serif1: Be sure to enhance your fighters.

name: Valdor
flavor_text: Many have come to my dojo to learn from me and to train their bodies and minds. But the reason I run my own dojo is to train myself. Now is the time to demonstrate the fruits of my training. I stand ready.
gacha_text: Unity is the greatest weapon for overcoming all odds. Let our hearts be one.
gacha_serif1: Unity is the greatest weapon for overcoming all odds. Let our hearts be one.

name: Valdor
flavor_text: Defeat... A word that rings with a familiar tune. But every time we were defeated, we rose again till the victory fanfare rang. This time, too, I swear: We will win in the end!
gacha_text: Victory and defeat. The difference is slight.
gacha_serif1: It always cheered me up and helped me overcome my loneliness.

name: Faerie (Brownie)
flavor_text: That Polka... At the beginning, I thought he was a useless little brat. Goes to show what some instruction from yours truly can do, huh?

name: Faerie (Brownie)
flavor_text: You think I'm satisfied with this small fry?! This ain't a catch. It's bait! Keep those peepers peeled. I'm gonna reel me in a massive monster!

name: Faerie (Brownie)
flavor_text: I... I wasn't always alone. There were others... many, many others like me!

name: Faerie (Brownie)
flavor_text: Faeries are good at music. Everyone knows that. The bagpipes can be tricky, but I'll show ya how it's done. All right, let's go! Whoa, this thing is loud! You could wake the dead.
gacha_text: I command thee to listen to my performance!
gacha_serif1: Don't try to smooth-talk me. You're not going to win me over like that.

name: Faerie (Brownie)
flavor_text: Y'know, it feels like I've been given the cold shoulder lately. You see anyone else who can move like me? Those Otherworld Warriors are a bunch of good-for-nothings! Leave everything to me!
gacha_text: Those Otherworld Warriors are a bunch of good-for-nothings!
gacha_serif1: Why I oughta! Get back here you stinkin' faerie!

name: Faerie (Brownie)
flavor_text: At first, I was alone. Then Zenon and Valdor helped me, and Polka and Liz got me involved in all the action... But that's not who I really am. So at the end of it all, I'll do this alone. Back to how I started.
gacha_text: I'm staying, no matter the cost!
gacha_serif1: You're not stealing the spotlight! I'm staying, no matter the cost!

name: Tu Kwai
flavor_text: We are cursed clumps of mud. Even our hearts have turned to mud in the face of a fate we could not escape. But the time has come for mud to crumble and fade. Time will march on, and new life will sprout in this land.
gacha_text: The time has come for mud to crumble and fade.
gacha_serif1: We became horrible creatures, kept alive by the curse.

name: Madeleine
flavor_text: It is a Gessian legend. When this flame goes out, the sun itself shall go out.

name: Madeleine
flavor_text: The true Khamsin is obtained by relinquishing what you hold dearest. That means the Khamsin has become more important to me than anything else. I have no regrets... Absolutely none!
gacha_text: I... chose the Khamsin.
gacha_serif1:
Art thou...
...Khamsin's successor?

name: Madeleine
flavor_text: I have a duty to lead the people of Gessiah. I cannot follow every word of Zenon's. If protecting Polka's family goes against the safety of my people, I will have to make a tough decision.

name: Madeleine
flavor_text: Khamsin, what do you wish of me? To expand the Naj Kingdom and start wars with neighboring kingdoms? To lead the people in living poor, yet peaceful lives? Or for me to be at the whim of the Child of Destiny? Tell me what it is exactly you want!
gacha_text: Khamsin, what do you wish of me?
gacha_serif1: Polka, Liz, Tatyana. I'm glad you came.

name: Madeleine
flavor_text: This is the Khamsin I got in the City of Kings, and this is the Khamsin Khalid entrusted to me. The coexistence of the two Khamsins is absurd. When this absurdity is resolved, the threads of destiny will surely be untangled.
gacha_text: One thing is clear... He's not a normal child.
gacha_serif1: One thing is clear... He's not a normal child.

name: Madeleine
flavor_text: How much of a sacrifice will it take to break through here? No, no life is worth losing. We will get through this without sacrificing a single life. That is a true breakthrough.
gacha_text: We will get through this without sacrificing a single life.

name: Zenon
flavor_text: Emperor Fegan of Messina hopes to destroy the Marquisate of Loanne by ordering Zenon to be put to death. However, the emperor's power has been undercut by a surge of people who oppose destroying post-Matriarchal Loanne.

name: Zenon
flavor_text: I've spent the 15 years since leaving the manor at Loanne alone in nature. The cries of the animals and the whispers of the wind point to every fabric that makes up this world. My path forward has been made clear to me.
gacha_text: My path forward has been made clear to me.

name: Zenon
flavor_text: All fates are converging and a new world is about to begin. I've done everything I needed to do as the Marquis of Loanne. All that remains is to witness the beginning of a new world as a mere man.
gacha_text: Vanguard must be protected at all costs.
gacha_serif1: Vanguard must be protected at all costs.

name: Zenon
flavor_text: I have dealt with the situation calmly as the Marquis of Loanne, as it was my duty to do so. But now I can act on the emotions that have welled up inside me!
gacha_text: I guess I was always so passionate. I feel I've reclaimed my true self.
gacha_serif1: On our lives, we must fulfill this duty.

name: Zenon
flavor_text: My heart yearned to make Loanne powerful once more. To be like Lord Mikhail, extolled through the ages. Deep inside, I rejoiced when the Graves appeared. It was a chance to find glory.
gacha_text: The future is in my hands.
gacha_serif1: I am Zenon Ausbach. Current ruler of Loanne, and head of the Grave Knights.

name: Dahao
flavor_text: Back then, Mamma said demons outside the cavern would use me for their own gain. And she was right. I'm sorry for not listening. I'm sorry I left you... all alone.

name: Dahao
flavor_text: O star spirits in the oracle water that gushes from the auspicious direction, give me your blessings! ...What's with these long chants? The star signs will show us the signs. Now, roll the dice for yourself.
gacha_text: Shen Du... Do it your own way, okay?
gacha_serif1: I said I wanted you to live, didn't I?

name: Witch's Daughter
flavor_text: There are things I cannot gain by simply continuing my research in the Wicked Witch's Cave. I must leave to get to the truth. Sorry I couldn't say goodbye, Mamma. I love you, Mamma.
gacha_text: I'll find what's missing and complete the Soul Inheritance ritual.
gacha_serif1: I... I must do this. I must fight.

name: Jo
flavor_text: I don't know what happened in the past, but if you really cared about me, you wouldn't have kept me away, Mother.

name: Jo
flavor_text: Uncle and Auntie used to be enemies in their old world. I'm not really sure if they get along now or not, but I can tell they need each other.
gacha_text: If you try to lose on purpose, I'll be furious.
gacha_serif1: My name is Josephine Lynn Wood, but everyone calls me Jo.

name: Jo
flavor_text: Even in costume, I have to be the strongest. So, I made a Genny costume with just a little help from others. I'll battle everyone in this. Man, this is gonna be fun!

name: Jo
flavor_text: I don't have full mastery over Genbu and Shucho arts, nor do I have the full powers of a mage yet. But I have to do it. Otherwise, I won't be able to protect Mom and Polka. Come on, Genny!
gacha_text: I don't wanna see anyone else die because of me.
gacha_serif1: I don't wanna see anyone else die because of me.

name: Jo
flavor_text: I thought I didn't care about destiny. But now, in this moment, I have to do everything I can. I have to protect Mom, Polka, Bert, everyone... This is my destiny.
gacha_text: I'm done letting insecurity hold me back.
gacha_serif1: Even if I did inherit the Archfiend's power and created Demon Towers...

name: Robingal
flavor_text: You have the right to choose your own destiny, even if you're an evildoer. Robin the Masked Crusader is a lover of freedom. So, which will it be for you? Hot or cold?
gacha_text: Robin the Masked Crusader is a lover of freedom.

name: Genryu
flavor_text: Water can take many forms. It can turn into a shield, like a mirror that reflects the enemy's attacks. The Mirror Shield... Just try and take it from me.

name: Genryu
flavor_text: I'm a dragon with the powers of both fire and water. Why was such a being brought into existence? Who knows, but the fact is that I do exist. She accepted me and everything I was born as. She never rejected me. I like her.
gacha_text: Are dragons rare?
gacha_serif1: Who goes there?

name: Genryu
flavor_text: Dragons are not meant to live with people. We've no reason to help them fight. And yet, I do. Why? It's because I have her. She accepted me, and I found comfort beside her.
gacha_text: We fight together.
gacha_serif1: Don't lose focus! There are more coming!

name: Bertrand
flavor_text: Josephine's strength lies in her conviction that she needs someone and that someone needs her. If only I'd met them sooner... Maybe I could also...

name: Bertrand
flavor_text: I've committed many sins and taken many lives. I don't deserve kindness, peace, or joy. I'll shun the sun, clothe myself in darkness, and give my life to the final battle.
gacha_text: New power awaits us in the Abyss.
gacha_serif1: Bertrand... That seems to be my name.

name: Bertrand
flavor_text: I lived only with the hope of bringing the world down with me. I've never thought about my future. I'm like a newborn now. Living day after day will be the trial for me.
gacha_text: I'll put an end to it my own way.
gacha_serif1: The next time we meet, it'll probably be in the final battle. Don't go dying, Josephine.

name: Genryu (Snowy)
flavor_text: He may be a foolish human who was enthralled by death and corrupted by darkness. But at that time, I felt that his lonesome heart was pure, like the frozen surface of a lake.
gacha_text: I shall stay by his side until his last breath.

name: Genryu (Snowy)
flavor_text: The humans said they were brother and sister. Then they entrusted us with something. They said it was more important than their lives, that it was irreplaceable...

name: Genryu (Snowy)
flavor_text: I cannot abide the otherworld demons that fill this world. Even more unforgivable is the one who summons them here. Our true enemy is the one who feeds them power and manipulates them. But as we cannot see the true enemy, we face these demons in vain.
gacha_text: We must fight our true enemy.

name: Igomahl
flavor_text: Look at these miserable and pathetic puppets in the palm of my hand. When they dance, the stars move to create the future I wish for. I am Igomahl the harlequin, puppeteer extraordinaire.

name: Igomahl
flavor_text: If you wanna quit, do it now. This merry-go-round will determine where you end up. It will be too late to regret it then. You still wanna see the vision?
gacha_text: See you around, cutie.
gacha_serif1: Such a clever and adorable child... I see potential.

name: Liam
flavor_text: I study. I eat good food. And then tomorrow comes. These are my peaceful days. The Door investigations make me nervous, but I'm not scared. After all, there's always tomorrow.

name: Liam
flavor_text: I always thought I'd spend my whole life in this city. I wonder what worlds await beyond the Doors, what kind of heroes I'll meet. It may be rash of me, but I'm super excited.
gacha_text: I'll help if I can!
gacha_serif1: Was that the test? Are you sure I shouldn't do anything else?

name: Liam
flavor_text: I'm not a rookie anymore. I've gained a lot of experience and seen my share of battles with the Otherworld Warriors. They've taught me the tricks of the trade. I know I can do this.
gacha_text: They're precious allies, and I want to fight alongside them.
gacha_serif1: I don't do it to get anything in return. I just want to do it.

name: Anya
flavor_text: I thought I could change if I went out into the world. Liam and the warriors have been so nice to me, even though I don't say much. Why, then, am I still so timid?

name: Anya
flavor_text: The voices of townspeople coming and going. The sound of musical instruments. The rustle of the trees. I'm now comforted by the things that used to frighten me. The world is filled with so much light.
gacha_text: Whatever happens, I want to be able to help all of you.
gacha_serif1: Would it be all right if I joined you?

name: Candy
flavor_text: Mee! Kyukyu kyuukyuu. Mew mewee mew mewee mewkyu kyu. Mew mew mew mew memememe kyu!

name: Candy
flavor_text: Welcome to Clavis! It's not much, but consider this your welcome party. Don't mind the little one who's already munching away. Though I suggest you grab something before it's all gone.
gacha_text: Mew mew
gacha_serif1: *meee*

name: Candy
flavor_text: Candy seems unhappy that people think the creature only thinks about food. But upon seeing Rocky's ice cream drawing, Candy gets an intense craving and can't help but reach for it. Peg just happens to be there.
gacha_text: Mew?! Kyukyu!
gacha_serif1: Mew mew.

name: Darius
flavor_text: Leader's just a role. I wouldn't say I'm special. Oh, but if the leader's the one protecting everyone on the front lines, that's a role I'll gladly take on.

name: Darius
flavor_text: Got our intel in order? Equipment all set? I'm taking some gold, too. Grab some emergency rations and water. You all understand your mission, yes? All right, let's go.
gacha_text: Great! We start tomorrow.
gacha_serif1: Liam. Welcome to the Survey Group Clavis. I'm the leader, Darius.

name: Barthelemy
flavor_text: I don't want you to be especially wealthy or famous. I just want you to be special to someone.

name: Barthelemy
flavor_text: Polka and Liz... Keep your eye on those two. They are an important part of this. Why are they important? Because they are chess pieces. Important chess pieces.
gacha_text: Oh Lil' Polka. How you've grown in such a short time.
gacha_serif1: I was born to be a killer.

name: Barthelemy
flavor_text: Clowns are here for the entertainment of others. But I'm different. I'm a clown for my own enjoyment. Everything is a show for my sake. And now, the curtain opens!
gacha_text: And now, the curtain opens!
gacha_serif1: Lil' Polka. How does it feel to be under the limelight once again?

name: Barthelemy
flavor_text: It's curious. The real me died when I learned the truth. This me was oblivious to it, hunting down Polka and Liz as a clown. As I face the truth, can I ever go back to being their father?
gacha_text: It's time you learn your fate.
gacha_serif1: Lil' Polka... There isn't much time.

name: Barthelemy
flavor_text: I just want you to grow up healthy. To have the energy and strength to do what you want to do. That's all you need to thrive. And one day, you will find someone special.
gacha_text: We share sadness and happiness as one family.
gacha_serif1: Ricota... Together we smile... Maha Ricota... Together we grin.

name: Melissa
flavor_text: You'll meet so many people in the future. Every encounter means something, but one of them will be extra special. I wonder when and where you will meet that special someone. What kind of person will they be?
gacha_text: We're going to make it. And I'm going to make you happy.
gacha_serif1: You know, I've been wondering for a while. What is that song?

name: Evelyn
flavor_text: I did not show myself during the disaster 600 years ago, nor did I leave my cave during the one 300 years ago. I did not sense the Archfiend's presence then.

name: Evelyn
flavor_text: Is it destiny that warps this world? Or is it the distortion of the world that creates destiny? It matters not. I exist in the rift between the distortions. When the threads of destiny are untangled, I shall vanish as well. It is time for the end.
gacha_text: I'm Evelyn... and this world is in flux.
gacha_serif1: I'm Evelyn... and this world is in flux.

name: Evelyn
flavor_text: Well, well. My old friends are here. Did they die with a grudge or with pride? Men or women, old or young, it matters not how they lived. Death comes to all. I am surrounded by death.
gacha_text: The blood given to me was from the Count of Podorui.

name: Wicked Witch
flavor_text: The Archfiend took everything from me, but I shall have my revenge. To approach the absolute evil that he is, I shall taint myself with evil. I shall gather girls with magical talent and taint them with evil as well. All for his demise!
gacha_text: I will never let anyone hurt my family ever again. Never!
gacha_serif1: They took everything away from me. My daughters. My family...

name: Sumire
flavor_text: Quick Blade! Ninjutsu: Swallow Throw! Eeeh, we're not done yet! Don't whine at just this level. Master's way, way stricter than I am!
gacha_text: Spark! I grasped an idea for a new training method! Just kidding.
gacha_serif1: Your announcer is Azami Dojo's resident little sister: Yours truly, Sumire!

name: Golden Baum
flavor_text: Mutated Golden Baum specimen, found in a Grave. Did the mutation come about from distortions in space and time that occur in Graves? Or did it travel here from a different dimension? We may never know...

name: Golden Baum
flavor_text: When I get into water, I start to spread out. It feels greeeat. Water is flowing through me, making me swell and expand. Water's the best!
gacha_text: Water is flowing through me, making me swell and expand. Water's the best!
gacha_serif1: What is this?! It's so fun!

name: Golden Baum
flavor_text: Spin, spin, SPIN! I spin like a top. I spin like a cow. I spin the umbrella, too. The more I spin, the more I stretch and streeetch. I'm stretchy like a rice cake! Happy! New! Year!
gacha_text: I'm stretchy like a rice cake! Happy! New! Year!

name: Golden Baum
flavor_text: Let's make chocolate together. Mix the cocoa, mix it again and again. Cocoa is not sweet. Add sugar, add more and more. Add some love, lots of love. The chocolate will be sweet for sure!
gacha_text: Ta-da! Aren't we adorable?!
gacha_serif1: You can thank me later with chocolate.

name: Minstrel
flavor_text: It is not the poems of gods but rather the words of the common people that ought to be sung in this land. Words flock to a soul that is at the mercy of an undeniable fate. Beautiful or foul, only truth can rouse the heart.
gacha_text: Will you listen to this tale?
gacha_serif1:
-Yes.
-No.
gacha_serif2: Shall I sing thee a story?

name: Minstrel
flavor_text: They say you'll find happiness if your first dream of the year is a good one. I say you can still be happy even if you have a nightmare. So, enjoy your first dream of the year!
gacha_text: So, enjoy your first dream of the year!

name: Minstrel
flavor_text: My repertoire is endless. I will hear any request. A tune for a friend, a song of joy, a melody of love, a nursery rhyme, a rousing battle song, and yes, that one, too.
gacha_text: I will hear any request.
gacha_serif1: Care for a tune?

name: Minstrel
flavor_text: The wonderful thing about jam sessions is you get to touch the musicians' souls. Each soul lights a fire in my heart. It's been a blast. Tonight is shaping up to be a good one.
gacha_text: Tonight is shaping up to be a good one.

name: ITOKEN
flavor_text: Let the holy melody play. Let the demonic rhythm be heard. Wring the captives' souls and give them to the damned. All are invited to the feast of the resurrected. Dance, scream, eat, purge, and then sleep.
gacha_text: Let the holy melody play. Let the demonic rhythm be heard.

name: Warmech
flavor_text: Danger. Danger. Intruder. Intruder. Get the intruders! Get them! Get them!
gacha_text: Intruder! Alert! Get them!
