gacha_serif1:
MACHINE attacks SQEX by BASH
220 damage

name: Albert
flavor_text: The hardest part about being left-handed is the fact that most weapons and armor are made for right-handed individuals. You right-handers probably won't understand the difference.

name: Final Emperor
flavor_text: The Imperial Throne has been passed on for generations. It contains all the aspirations of past emperors. This is what it means to sit on the throne. Should I fail, all those aspirations come to naught. This heavy burden will give me strength.
gacha_text:
Stop calling me Your Majesty. I
am the emperor no more.

name: Asellus
flavor_text: I always wondered who I really was. Was I human? Mystic? Neither? But I had no need to wonder. I am Asellus. And that's all I need to know.
gacha_text:
I'm me. I like me. I've realized
that's good enough for me.

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: Flavor text TBD

name: Liz Lynn Wood
flavor_text: Flavor text TBD

name: Professor
flavor_text: Flavor text TBD

name: Claudia
flavor_text: I'm on the lookout for anyone suspicious in the festival. However, the task is getting tedious. I wonder if there's anything else I can aim my arrow at... If I were the type of person who would say, "I'll shoot you through the heart!" I might be able to live more freely.
gacha_text: I'll give it my best shot!

name: Barbara
flavor_text: There is an end to every performance and a limit to the time we have, but they are steps to my next stage. Let's pump it up and end with a bang!
gacha_text: Let's pump it up and end with a bang!

name: Diana (RS1/MS)
flavor_text: My brother is alive. It is his mission to survive. I have taught him strictly that as a noble, he must fulfill his mission. That is why he must still be out there somewhere. I am sure he is alive.
gacha_text: Albert!
gacha_serif1: I'm searching for my missing brother.

name: Neidhart
flavor_text: It is said that the evil god Saruin was sealed by the knight Mirsa himself. But how could a mere mortal, no matter how heroic, seal a god? The answer to my long-standing question lies ahead.
gacha_text: It takes courage to seek the truth.
gacha_serif1: Life in the Crystal Palace can be stifling. I want you to take me on an adventure.

name: Darque
flavor_text: Approaching from an unexpected direction. This is an essential move for assassination. With this, success is 100% assured. Whether or not you can escape afterwards is another matter. If you can't manage to escape, take your life. That's what an assassin does.
gacha_text: Approaching from an unexpected direction. This is an essential move for assassination. With this, success is 100% assured.
gacha_serif1: Saruin is our common enemy. I would be delighted to lend you a hand.

name: Silver
flavor_text: Even the great and revered don't realize that I have the power of a dragon within me. It felt so good to blast away that smirkin' big scallywag with a single blow when he let his guard down!
gacha_text: There are no rules against usin' me dragon powers, savvy? This ain't cheatin'.

name: Leon
flavor_text:
Now, here's to everyone's health. Cheers!
Here's to a bountiful harvest. Cheers!
And, here's to victory tomorrow. Cheers!
gacha_text: Drink up!
gacha_serif1: The return of the Seven Heroes won't bring about peace any time soon. Battles will ensue.

name: Final Emperor
flavor_text: The threat of the Seven Heroes is no more. My duty and those of the generations of emperors before me have come to an end. The time has come to free ourselves from Emperor Leon's long-standing wishes. We dedicate this evening's banquet to all the emperors who led us here. Let us enjoy one last moment together.
gacha_text: Everything will end. That's something to rejoice about.

name: Final Empress
flavor_text: I have put an end to the ambitions of the Seven Heroes for the good of the people of the Varennes Empire. My duty to carry on the wishes of the emperors is at an end. I wish now for a new purpose.
gacha_text: I am no longer the empress.

name: Coppelia
flavor_text: Be prepared for everything. Such is the duty of the Empress of Varennes. If I trip and fall, all my subjects will have to fall with me. There, now I'm ready to dance with a light step.
gacha_text: It would be so wonderful if the Empress only had to dance.
gacha_serif1: I am now the Empress. I've inherited the soul of the last Emperor, and thus have been granted true life.

name: Therese
flavor_text: Aim nice and steady, and don't you miss. I want to see how good you are. I'll give you a pose so you get a better shot. All right, go for it. (I don't need a bow and arrow to hunt for this prey.)
gacha_text: Here. If you're going to aim, aim here.

name: Emerald
flavor_text: Oh, you're awake. You're buried in sand up to your neck. Do you understand your situation? You're a million years too early to be hitting on me. Just bake in the sun like that for a while longer.
gacha_text: If you're going to hit on someone, at least bring a little something. Be thoughtful.

name: Emerald
flavor_text: I am tireless in my studies of the Fire Arts. I train in real battles like this. Other kinds of spells? Well, hehe...

name: Minerva
flavor_text: Plant your spear on the ground and do a pole-vault kick! I bet you never imagined using it like this. There is no weapon more versatile than the spear. The spear is the strongest.
gacha_text: I'll fight to my last breath!
gacha_serif1:
Add to party.
Decline.

name: Azami
flavor_text: A ninja lives for the mission. The greater the mission, the more fulfilling life becomes. Even if I have to meet my end fighting a mighty foe, I have no regrets about my way of life.
gacha_text: A ninja lives for the mission.

name: Vampire Lady
flavor_text: I've always spent my time doing what I love, not what I'm obligated to do. But you have to be serious about what you love to really enjoy it, right? So, it's time to get serious from now on.
gacha_text: I'll suck all your blood!
gacha_serif1: Do you know just how enticing the nape of your neck is? I need to take a bite.

name: Rocbouquet
flavor_text: Beauty that blossoms in an instant is but fleeting. To me, you resemble these fireworks, dream-like and fantastical. So please allow me to engrave in my memory the image of your face as it shines in the bright blooms of the fireworks.
gacha_text: I don't know if we can usher in a new day together, so we should cherish this moment.

name: Mikhail
flavor_text: Attacking the enemy at sunrise is strategically better than making a night attack. First of all, nighttime operations are prone to accidents. Secondly, soldiers are less tired in the morning. And finally, the rising sun will blind the enemy and give us an advantage. All charge!
gacha_text: All charge!
gacha_serif1: Please give us orders!

name: Monika
flavor_text: Fear of death, loss, and the unknown. While I cannot escape these fears, I know they are but mere feelings, and there is nothing more I need to fear.
gacha_text: Good luck, Brother!
gacha_serif1: Katarina, there's trouble!
gacha_serif2: Is there something wrong, Lady Monika?

name: Katarina
flavor_text: I won't forgive you for peeking a look. And no, that's not all. I was just relaxing by myself here, but you ruined that, too. Just wait there while I wring out my shirt. Hey, where are you looking? ...You don't seem to be sorry at all.
gacha_text: Hey, where are you looking?

name: Katarina
flavor_text: Long hair is required of a lady of nobility. Before I cut it myself, I didn't think it to be anything special, but I was wrong. The length symbolizes a readiness to shoulder the weight of longstanding noble traditions.
gacha_text: Long hair is high-maintenance. Still, I decide to grow it long. Don't forget what that means.
gacha_serif1:
You receive relics of the Matriarch!
Staff of Glory.
Masquerade.

name: Katarina
flavor_text: I have been charged with protecting Lady Monika as she attends her awards ceremony. This uniform is, of course, for that mission. She demanded it be a little showy... so my outfit's a little... extravagant.
gacha_text: It was your courage, Milady, that ensured our success against Godwin.
gacha_serif1: It was your courage, Milady, that ensured our success against Godwin.
gacha_serif2: As always, thank you, Katarina.

name: Tatyana
flavor_text: You're my only friend. If you leave me here, I'll really be all alone. So please, don't ever, ever, ever let go of my hand.
gacha_text: I'm not running away anymore!
gacha_serif1: I'm used to that.

name: Rukh
flavor_text: I heard tales of creatures like Rukh with four legs. Are they like centaurs? They can't be walking on their hands, crawling everywhere. Ridiculous! We have two legs. Two!
gacha_text: Rukh only has and needs two legs.
gacha_serif1: Now that Big Bro's better, guess I'll head out and see the world.

name: Undine
flavor_text: The highlight of this festival is fire. It illuminates the lanterns and makes them float into the night sky. But if we wrap water around the fire, we can turn it into a water festival where water sprinkles down onto the ground.
gacha_text: The lights are beautiful, aren't they?

name: Maiden of Lance
flavor_text: Every day is a trial, but I survived yesterday. I also survived today. So I'll probably survive tomorrow, too. But I don't think about the future too much. After all, I don't know if I'll survive the day after tomorrow.

name: Red
flavor_text: To change into Alkaiser from Red takes only one millisecond, so it's impossible to take a photo of me while I'm changing. That means what you have here is a fake photo. But if this photo is real, then someone's memory is about to be erased.
gacha_text: Now that you all remember me, it's time I go all out!
gacha_serif1: Alkaiser Change!

name: Alkaiser
flavor_text: I got a large bowl of the famous Champon noodles as a thank me for my service. This is the best! But the only way to eat it is to unmorph, so do I just grab and run? That's not very hero-like! Ahh, what to do?!
gacha_text: A hero's biggest weakness: eating and drinking.

name: Emelia
flavor_text: Being a spokesperson for an arms dealer is definitely not my thing, because I don't need a gun to shoot you through the heart.
gacha_text: I have work to do.
gacha_serif1: Start

name: Asellus
flavor_text: Even before I accepted the Mystic blood, I was lost. Will I grow up? Will I change? I faced him, and things ended up this way, but I still can't figure it out. Have I grown up?
gacha_text: Another... "me"? Which me would that be?
gacha_serif1: I know this is my fate, and I accept it.

name: Fuse
flavor_text: The name's Lostar. I am an IRPO detective. Just call me Fuse like everyone else. I mean, I've got a bit of a short fuse, but I'm the top member in the Region Patrol. Top in absences, salary advances, number of apology letters... Oh wait, that's not what I meant.
gacha_text: Why'd you shoot him?!
gacha_serif1: He was a friend from my school days, and we knew each other for 10 years. He was always so serious. Unlike me.

name: Doll
flavor_text: I wanted you to run into the sea. This way, I can enjoy water sports while I'm on duty. And I don't have to worry about Fuse's creepy glances here. So, thanks for this!
gacha_text: I wanted you to run into the sea. This way, I can enjoy water sports while I'm on duty.

name: Cotton
flavor_text: "That Fuse came up with the best plan ever. This way, we can round up all the bad guys. I can also get recognition for my performance and a bonus from the management. I'll have to treat him to a nice meal." I know that's what you were saying. Right, Cotton?
gacha_text: "That Fuse came up with the best plan ever."
gacha_serif1: Kyu!
gacha_serif2: I'm sorry, Detective Cotton. I want you keeping watch on the back alleys of Koorong.

name: Roufas
flavor_text: Your work this time is highly appreciated by the heads of Gladius. That's why we're here on vacation. I'm rewarding you with a portion of the supplies we have obtained. There you go. Don't drop it!
gacha_text: It's the commander's job to boost the morale of his team. Take it easy once in a while.

name: Annie
flavor_text: Mm-hmm, I'm actually a pretty good artist. I should paint a portrait of Roufas! People will love it, I'm sure. But why am I so messy before I even start?
gacha_text: I guess I'll paint the beauties of nature?

name: Lyza
flavor_text: The moment I take off my wetsuit, I feel the wind on my skin. It's such an exhilarating feeling. It sure feels great on the waves and in the sea, but this is a different kind of pleasure.
gacha_text: I'm all sweaty in the wetsuit.

name: Rouge
flavor_text: My magic is for defeating him. This is not the way it should be used, but if I can entertain you and give everyone hope for the New Year, perhaps it's not a bad thing.
gacha_text: Let's make butterflies dance.

name: Princess White Rose
flavor_text: I'm Princess Pumpkin. A pumpkin is much too heavy to wear as a hat, but I think I've done my best to match the motif. I wonder what he would call me if he saw this outfit?
gacha_text: Pumpkins and roses have their ways of life. It pleases me to say that both are wonderful.
gacha_serif1: Just call me White Rose.

name: Urpina
flavor_text: No one else is here yet, you say? This is everyone. It's an evening of gratitude dedicated to you, so you are the only guest. I shall be hosting and serving you all by myself.
gacha_text: It's an evening of gratitude dedicated to you.

name: Urpina
flavor_text: It is still bitter cold, and there is snow everywhere, but it's times like this that I enjoy looking for signs of spring. The plum trees look cold, but they sure know that spring is coming. Behold, they blossom here and there.
gacha_text: There are buds over here.

name: Urpina
flavor_text: I'm trying to emulate Elysed's fashion sense. I aspire to be like her--a wonderful lady who's to be married to such an amazing man as my brother.

name: Leonard (SSG)
flavor_text: It's getting annoying. They all want gifts. Guess I'll just make it quick. Hey, you there! I'll throw you the gift. You better catch it!
gacha_text: It's getting annoying. They all want gifts.

name: Elisabeth
flavor_text: I'm not stingy when it comes to showing off my figure. If you want a look, go for it. No big deal. But in exchange, you WILL have to do what I say. Naturally, nothing is free in this world.
gacha_text: Hey, can you put some sunscreen on me?

name: Sasha
flavor_text: Don't ask me what I'm doing. I can't explain it to you, but this is how I relax. Please be quiet and don't bother me.
gacha_text: Being in a lively environment is not bad, but I feel most comfortable when I'm alone.

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: That's his name. We're always together. He may look small, but when I'm in trouble, he gets bigger and saves me! He protects Mom and Dad, too! Roarrr!

name: Zenon
flavor_text: With the maritime mobile fortress Vanguard taken away, we lost a third of our land. Houses and facilities built on Vanguard's surface were also gone. For our grieving citizens, we must hasten the restoration.

name: Jo
flavor_text: I'll run the marathon on foot--no magic. No pressure though, just run at your own pace. I want you to finish the race, but if you're having a hard time, you have to be brave and stop halfway. Let's enjoy the marathon together!
